{"type":"message","id":"1380701d","parentId":"59e3c166","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:56:35.802Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create the Memory.md entity page.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d78526f1bcc5713ddad19e24b3520","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Memory\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [memory, storage, knowledge-base]\n---\n\n# 🧠 Memory\n\n> OpenClaw 记忆系统\n\n## 系统架构\n\n```\nMEMORY.md (入口)\n    ├── memory/preferences.md      (用户偏好)\n    ├── memory/projects/           (项目知识)\n    │   └── openclaw.md\n    ├── memory/knowledge.md        (固化知识)\n    ├── memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md       (每日日志)\n    ├── memory/ephemeral/          (临时记忆，自动清理)\n    ├── memory/ontology/           (知识图谱)\n    └── memory/entities/           (实体页 - 新增)\n```\n\n## 核心规则\n\n| 规则 | 描述 |\n|------|------|\n| 对话说过的话 = 忘记 | 会话级记忆 |\n| 写进文件的内容 = 永远记得 | 持久化记忆 |\n| 每次纠正 → 写入 ~/self-improving/ | 错误修正沉淀 |\n| 学到新东西 → 写入 ~/self-improving/ | 学习沉淀 |\n\n## 工具链\n\n### 搜索\n\n```bash\nopenclaw memory search \"关键词\"\n```\n\n技术实现：\n- provider: openai\n- model: text-embedding-3-small\n- mode: hybrid (关键词 + 向量)\n\n### 读取\n\n```bash\n# 读取 MEMORY.md\nmemory_get path=MEMORY.md\n\n# 读取指定文件\nmemory_get path=memory/entities/openclaw.md\n```\n\n## 当前存量\n\n| 类型 | 数量 |\n|------|------|\n| 每日记忆 | ~30 个 |\n| 实体页 | 5 个（新建） |\n| 项目页 | 1 个 |\n| 固化知识 | 1 个 |\n\n---\n\n## Wiki 化改进 (2026-04-11)\n\n参照 [LLM Wiki 模式](./2026-04-10-second-brain.md)，正在进行结构重构：\n\n### 新增实体页\n\n| 页面 | 路径 |\n|------|------|\n| OpenClaw | `entities/openclaw.md` |\n| Skills | `entities/skills.md` |\n| Memory | `entities/memory.md` (本文) |\n| Model | `entities/model.md` |\n| Feishu | `entities/feishu.md` |\n\n### 改进方向\n\n1. **从日期驱动 → 实体驱动**\n   - 旧：按日期记录 (2026-04-10.md)\n   - 新：每个概念独立页面 (OpenClaw.md)\n\n2. **引入跨引用**\n   - 页面间通过 `[[PageName]]` 链接\n\n3. **Ingest 流程**\n   - 重要对话 → 自动生成/更新实体页\n\n4. **定期 Lint**\n   - 检查矛盾、过时、孤儿页面\n\n---\n\n## 路径速查\n\n| 用途 | 路径 |\n|------|------|\n| 主入口 | `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md` |\n| 每日日志 | `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/` |\n| 自我改进 | `~/self-improving/` |\n| 主动性状态 | `~/proactivity/` |\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[OpenClaw]] — 主项目\n- [[Skills]] — 技能系统\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/memory.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":7225,"output":771,"cacheRead":23296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31292,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775840160804,"responseId":"019d785265daedcddb9814ebd977e76e"}}
