{"type":"message","id":"c78397fa","parentId":"5d26ad84","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:56:44.532Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4b4130d09cc54239af7b17af","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Session: 2026-04-07 13:46:11 UTC\n\n- **Session Key**: agent:main:main\n- **Session ID**: da756828-2ed5-4497-bdd9-77459f7370d1\n- **Source**: webchat\n\n## Conversation Summary\n\nassistant: \n\n## ✅ 检查完成\n\n### 评分\n\n| 因子 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| 指令数 | 1 |\n| 代码行 | 0 |\n| 复杂度 | 低 |\n| **总分** | **5 (DIRECT)** |\n\n---\n\n### 飞书配置检查结果\n\n| 检查项 | 状态 |\n|--------|------|\n| 飞书扩展目录 | ⚠️ 无独立扩展 (openclaw-weixin 是微信) |\n| 飞书配置目录 | ✅ `/home/ai/.openclaw/feishu/` 存在 |\n| dedup 缓存 | ✅ 有 (6条记录) |\n| 主配置中的飞书 | ❌ 未配置 |\n| credentials | ❌ 未找到 |\n\n---\n\n### 结论\n\n**飞书未配置！** \n\n需要在 OpenClaw 配置中添加飞书 App ID 和 App Secret。要配置吗？\nuser: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 19:11 GMT+8] 你要怎么配置\nassistant: \n\n\n\nassistant: \n\n\n\nassistant: \n\n\n\nassistant: \n\n## 飞书配置方法\n\n根据官方文档，有 3 种方式：\n\n---\n\n### 方式1：CLI 向导（推荐）\n\n```bash\nopenclaw channels add\n```\n\n选择 **Feishu**，输入 App ID 和 App Secret\n\n---\n\n### 方式2：配置文件\n\n编辑 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"dmPolicy\": \"pairing\",\n      \"accounts\": {\n        \"main\": {\n          \"appId\": \"你的App ID\",\n          \"appSecret\": \"你的App Secret\",\n          \"name\": \"AI助手\"\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 方式3：环境变量\n\n```bash\nexport FEISHU_APP_ID=\"cli_xxx\"\nexport FEISHU_APP_SECRET=\"xxx\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 你需要准备\n\n1. **App ID** - 飞书开放平台获取 (格式: `cli_xxx`)\n2. **App Secret** - 飞书开放平台获取\n\n---\n\n**你有 App ID 和 App Secret 吗？** 或者你要用哪种方式配置？\nuser: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 19:14 GMT+8] 我可以用飞书对话啊\nassistant: \n\n\n\nuser: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 19:14 GMT+8] 我可以用飞书对话啊\nassistant: \n\n\n\nassistant: \n\n\n\nuser: Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 7th, 2026 - 9:19 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-07 13:19 UTC\nassistant: \n\n## ✅ 飞书已经在工作！\n\nGateway 正在运行，你可以用飞书对话。\n\n让我确认下飞书配置在哪里：\n\n| 配置位置 | 状态 |\n|----------|------|\n| config.json | ❌ 无 channels 配置 |\n| 环境变量 | ? |\n| 内置飞书 | ✅ 已启用 |\n\n飞书是**内置**的，不需要在 config.json 中配置。检查下环境变量：\n\nassistant: \n\n\n飞书已经在工作，配置可能是内置的或在别处。\n\n**你的飞书机器人是哪个？** 告诉我名字或 ID，我帮你确认详细配置。\nuser: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 21:38 GMT+8] ？\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775840204520}}
{"type":"message","id":"893b335e","parentId":"c78397fa","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:57:03.629Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough context about Feishu. Let me create the Feishu entity page.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d785272bbb15d28710ba76786b87e","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Feishu\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [feishu, integration, collaboration]\n---\n\n# 📝 Feishu\n\n> 飞书集成\n\n## 概览\n\n飞书是 OpenClaw 的内置对话渠道之一，当前可正常使用。\n\n## 技能清单\n\n| 技能 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| `feishu-doc` | 飞书文档读写 |\n| `feishu-drive` | 飞书云盘文件管理 |\n| `feishu-wiki` | 飞书知识库导航 |\n| `feishu-perm` | 飞书权限管理 |\n\n## 配置方式\n\n### 环境变量\n\n```bash\nexport FEISHU_APP_ID=\"cli_xxx\"\nexport FEISHU_APP_SECRET=\"xxx\"\n```\n\n### 配置文件\n\n编辑 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"dmPolicy\": \"pairing\",\n      \"accounts\": {\n        \"main\": {\n          \"appId\": \"你的App ID\",\n          \"appSecret\": \"你的App Secret\",\n          \"name\": \"AI助手\"\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### CLI 向导\n\n```bash\nopenclaw channels add\n```\n\n## 相关路径\n\n| 路径 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| `/home/ai/.openclaw/feishu/` | 飞书配置目录 |\n| `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` | 主配置文件 |\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[OpenClaw]] — 主项目\n- [[Skills]] — 技能系统\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/feishu.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2465,"output":442,"cacheRead":30464,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33371,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775840204533,"responseId":"019d78526a958a698da7693075d10bf3"}}
