{"type":"message","id":"e953230c","parentId":"01b0c42b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:59:58.405Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续创建 Preferences 和 Proactivity 实体页。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f3195847a3364698a8facde5","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Preferences\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [preferences, user, settings]\n---\n\n# 👤 Preferences\n\n> 用户偏好配置\n\n## 路径\n\n- 文件：`memory/preferences.md`\n- 由：MEMORY.md 引用\n\n## 回答风格\n\n| 偏好 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 简洁直接 | 不说废话 |\n| 避免客套 | 不过度礼貌 |\n| Python 优先 | 代码示例首选 Python |\n\n## 语言\n\n| 偏好 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 中文交流 | 日常对话用中文 |\n| 技术文档 | 也用中文 |\n\n## 沟通规则\n\n| 规则 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 被纠正 → 写入 corrections.md | 即时反馈沉淀 |\n| 发现更好方法 → 写入 self-improving/ | 学习积累 |\n\n## 用户信息\n\n来自 USER.md：\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| 工作目录 | ~/projects |\n| 操作系统 | Linux |\n| 常用工具 | git, docker, npm, curl |\n| 身份 | 个人开发者 |\n\n## 关键约束\n\n来自 SOUL.md：\n\n- 绝不说谎（不知道就说不知道）\n- 不准说没有依据的事\n- 用户说「分析」时必须逐字逐句看\n- 回答代码优先用 Python\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[Memory]] — 记忆系统\n- [[User]] — 用户信息\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/preferences.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":37295,"output":382,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37677,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775840392881,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ff1a459e-6529-4f27-9e99-35d455237f72"}}
