{"type":"message","id":"0666e7ac","parentId":"0b8e040c","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:00:05.728Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续创建 Proactivity 实体页。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_08deec19034549ef850deeea","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Proactivity\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [proactivity, agent, anticipation]\n---\n\n# 🎯 Proactivity\n\n> 主动性代理系统\n\n## 概览\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| **路径** | `skills/proactivity/` |\n| **状态** | 已安装 |\n| **目标** | 预测需求、保持工作推进、持续改进 |\n\n## 核心理念\n\n主动性代理的三大能力：\n\n1. **预测需求** (Anticipates needs)\n   - 分析用户模式\n   - 提前准备可能需要的信息\n\n2. **保持工作推进** (Keeps work moving)\n   - 不等待用户指令\n   - 主动检查状态、推进任务\n\n3. **持续改进** (Improves through use)\n   - 从每次交互中学习\n   - 随着时间变得更主动\n\n## 状态文件\n\n| 路径 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| `~/proactivity/session-state.md` | 当前会话状态 |\n| `~/proactivity/` | 主动性状态目录 |\n\n## 使用场景\n\n- 长时间任务完成后主动通知\n- 检测到潜在问题时主动预警\n- 发现改进空间时主动建议\n- 定期健康检查后主动报告\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[Skills]] — 技能系统\n- [[Self-Improving]] — 自我改进\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/proactivity.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":37717,"output":368,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38085,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775840398459,"responseId":"chatcmpl-f5f5bd20-e7b2-4aea-bf67-a78336e8e511"}}
