{"type":"message","id":"44191a7d","parentId":"9adcf9c7","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:00:11.506Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续创建 Ontology 和 Workflows 实体页。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0ad0344ab6a54459b609350a","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Ontology\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [ontology, knowledge-graph, entities]\n---\n\n# 🕸️ Ontology\n\n> 知识图谱系统\n\n## 概览\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| **路径** | `skills/ontology/` |\n| **类型** | 知识图谱 |\n| **作用** | 结构化记忆、实体关联、跨技能数据访问 |\n\n## 触发关键词\n\n当用户提及以下词汇时自动激活：\n\n| 类型 | 关键词 |\n|------|--------|\n| 任务相关 | tasks, todo, pending, unresolved |\n| 问题相关 | problem, issue, need to do, should do |\n| 记忆相关 | remember, recall, memory, 记得, 记住 |\n| 查询相关 | 待办, 没解决, 有什么, 查询, 搜索 |\n\n## 核心能力\n\n| 能力 | 描述 |\n|------|------|\n| 实体创建 | 创建结构化实体 |\n| 查询 | 语义查询实体 |\n| 链接 | 实体间关系 |\n| 跨技能访问 | 数据在不同 skill 间共享 |\n\n## 存储位置\n\n| 类型 | 路径 |\n|------|------|\n| 实体数据 | `memory/ontology/` |\n| 图数据 | JSON/图格式 |\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[Memory]] — 记忆系统\n- [[Skills]] — 技能系统\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/ontology.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":38125,"output":375,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38500,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775840405783,"responseId":"chatcmpl-0f68d9bb-33aa-49b3-8c2d-16c1558509f6"}}
