{"type":"message","id":"14823302","parentId":"b5f3d3be","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:01:29.545Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完美！现在有12个实体页了。让我给用户一个总结。\n\n页面列表：\n1. openclaw.md - 主项目\n2. skills.md - 技能系统\n3. memory.md - 记忆系统\n4. model.md - 模型配置\n5. feishu.md - 飞书集成\n6. claude-code.md - Claude Code 学习\n7. task-orchestrator.md - 任务编排\n8. self-improving.md - 自我改进\n9. preferences.md - 用户偏好\n10. proactivity.md - 主动性代理\n11. ontology.md - 知识图谱\n12. workflows.md - 自动化工作流\n\n现在Wiki化已经比较完整了。让我给用户一个简洁的总结。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n完成。新增 7 个实体页：\n\n| 页面 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| `claude-code.md` | Claude Code 架构、工具系统、学习记录 |\n| `task-orchestrator.md` | 任务评分、6因子评分、策略路由 |\n| `self-improving.md` | 自我改进规则、文件结构、工作流 |\n| `preferences.md` | 用户偏好、回答风格、语言规则 |\n| `proactivity.md` | 主动性代理理念、状态文件 |\n| `ontology.md` | 知识图谱、触发关键词 |\n| `workflows.md` | 自动化工作流、工具箱 |\n\n## 当前实体页总数：12 个\n\n```\nentities/\n├── openclaw.md          # 主项目\n├── skills.md            # 技能系统 (29个)\n├── memory.md            # 记忆系统\n├── model.md             # 模型配置\n├── feishu.md            # 飞书集成\n├── claude-code.md       # Claude Code 学习\n├── task-orchestrator.md # 任务编排\n├── self-improving.md    # 自我改进\n├── preferences.md       # 用户偏好\n├── proactivity.md       # 主动性代理\n├── ontology.md          # 知识图谱\n└── workflows.md         # 自动化工作流\n```\n\nWiki 化骨架已搭建，下一步：建立 ingest 流程？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":40279,"output":440,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40719,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775840483496,"responseId":"chatcmpl-07ef77b9-b45d-470c-a914-3f7a414bb6e1"}}
