{"type":"message","id":"21e408e1","parentId":"85974395","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:03:21.213Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想看两个选项的优缺点对比。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n| 选项 | 优点 | 缺点 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **A. Schema** | 结构规范、可复用、团队共享 | 初期投入大、可能过度设计 |\n| **B. Ingest 实战** | 快速见效、边做边迭代、更贴合实际需求 | 可能需要后期重构、有技术债风险 |\n\n**建议**：B 先行，实践中总结规律，再沉淀成 Schema。这样是 \"let the code evolve\" 的思路。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":40303,"output":110,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40413,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775840598610,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d5ebd12f-6179-4a67-9e6e-581a9e9fc32b"}}
