{"type":"message","id":"20da7bbb","parentId":"cf7ecbcb","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:06:39.140Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me provide a summary to the user.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**Lint 机制已启用并完成首次检查**\n\n## 首次 Lint 结果\n\n| 检查项 | 状态 |\n|--------|------|\n| 实体页总数 | 16 个 |\n| 有效链接 | 12 |\n| 修复死链 | 3 个 ✅ |\n\n## 修复内容\n\n| 问题 | 修复 |\n|------|------|\n| [[Claude Code]] | 改为 [[claude-code]] |\n| [[LLM Wiki]] | 改为 [[llm-wiki]] |\n| [[User]] 缺失 | 创建 user.md |\n\n## 完整实体页清单 (16)\n\n```\nentities/\n├── openclaw.md\n├── skills.md\n├── memory.md\n├── model.md\n├── feishu.md\n├── claude-code.md\n├── task-orchestrator.md\n├── self-improving.md\n├── preferences.md\n├── proactivity.md\n├── ontology.md\n├── workflows.md\n├── ingest.md      # 新增\n├── lint.md        # 新增\n├── llm-wiki.md    # 新增\n└── user.md        # 新增\n```\n\nWiki 健康检查已就绪。此后可定期运行 lint。要继续完善其他方面，还是开始日常使用？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":45234,"output":259,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45493,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775840795172,"responseId":"chatcmpl-75280294-133a-45d8-a316-7873d08351f5"}}
