{"type":"message","id":"15b15588","parentId":"87d802a5","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:12:14.776Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create the raw sources management page and update the wiki structure.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_972a3ca4537d4916a85772b1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Raw Sources\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [raw-sources, documents, input]\n---\n\n# 📂 Raw Sources\n\n> 原始文档库（不可变）\n\n## 目录结构\n\n```\nraw/\n├── articles/    # 网络文章（通过 Web Clipper 获取）\n├── papers/      # 论文、报告\n├── notes/       # 临时笔记（待处理）\n└── assets/      # 图片等附件\n```\n\n## 管理规则\n\n| 规则 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 不可变 | LLM 只读，不修改原始文件 |\n| 精选 | 只放值得处理的源 |\n| 带日期 | 文件名加日期前缀 |\n\n## 摄取流程\n\n```\n1. 放入 raw/ 目录\n2. 执行 Ingest\n3. LLM 提取要点 → 写入 wiki\n4. 原始文件保留在 raw/\n```\n\n## 工具推荐\n\n### Web Clipper\n- 使用 Obsidian Web Clipper 浏览器插件\n- 一键将网页转为 markdown\n\n### 图片下载\n- Obsidian 设置 → Attachment folder path → `raw/assets/`\n- 绑定热键 Ctrl+Shift+D 下载所有图片\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[ingest]] — 摄取流程\n- [[wiki-schema]] — Schema 规范\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/raw-sources.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":48489,"output":361,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48850,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775841129370,"responseId":"chatcmpl-53bde0e0-0f95-4e5e-b3c5-a1b53b0d8e2f"}}
