{"type":"message","id":"ba22f17b","parentId":"698562f9","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:13:51.394Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me finalize by listing the entities again.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n全部完成。\n\n## 新增内容\n\n| 补全项 | 实施 |\n|--------|------|\n| Raw Sources 目录 | 创建 `raw/{articles,papers,notes,assets}/` |\n| raw-sources.md | 源文件管理规范 |\n| log.md | 统一时间线格式 |\n| Obsidian 配置 | obsidian.md |\n| qmd 搜索 | search.md |\n| 答案写回 | 更新 ingest.md，添加 Query Write-back |\n| 自动化扩散 | Ingest 时更新 10-15 个页面的规范 |\n\n## 当前实体页总数：22 个\n\n```\nentities/\n├── openclaw.md\n├── skills.md\n├── memory.md\n├── model.md\n├── feishu.md\n├── claude-code.md\n├── task-orchestrator.md\n├── self-improving.md\n├── preferences.md\n├── proactivity.md\n├── ontology.md\n├── workflows.md\n├── ingest.md         (增强)\n├── lint.md\n├── llm-wiki.md\n├── wiki-schema.md\n├── second-brain-report.md\n├── user.md\n├── raw-sources.md    (新增)\n├── log.md            (新增)\n├── obsidian.md       (新增)\n└── search.md         (新增)\n```\n\nWiki 模式已完整对齐 LLM Wiki 原文。现在可以：\n1. 把网页文章放入 `raw/` → 自动 Ingest\n2. 重要问答 → 写回 wiki\n3. 用 Obsidian 实时浏览"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1437,"output":309,"cacheRead":50816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52562,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775841210581,"responseId":"019d78626381598e7661b8cfdf37b823"}}
