{"type":"message","id":"4a37728b","parentId":"fefde5a9","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:14:42.843Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to think more deeply and check what's still missing or could be improved. Let me re-read the LLM Wiki document again and compare against what I've implemented.\n\nKey items from the original LLM Wiki that I may have missed:\n\n1. **Contradictions handling** - \"noting where new data contradicts old claims\" - I mentioned this in Lint but didn't create a specific workflow\n\n2. **Stronger/weaker claims** - \"strengthening or challenging the evolving synthesis\" - not implemented\n\n3. **Marp slides** - generating presentations from wiki - mentioned Obsidian but not full integration\n\n4. **Dataview** - mentioned but not integrated into workflow\n\n5. **The \"comparison\" output format** - \"A comparison you asked for, an analysis, a connection you discovered — these are valuable and shouldn't disappear into chat history\"\n\n6. **The core philosophy** - The wiki is a \"persistent, compounding artifact\" - need to ensure this mindset is reflected\n\n7. **The human's job** - \"curate sources, direct the analysis, ask good questions, and think about what it all means\" - should I create a page about this?\n\n8. **Personal applications** mentioned in the doc:\n   - Personal: goals, health, psychology, self-improvement\n   - Research: going deep on a topic\n   - Reading a book\n   - Business/team: internal wiki\n   - Competitive analysis, due diligence, trip planning, course notes\n\nLet me check what I might have missed and create additional content.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_09e936fd02824182b8989c39","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"LLM Wiki pattern Memex synthesis contradiction","maxResults":3}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":52314,"output":363,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52677,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775841277068,"responseId":"chatcmpl-5eabe65e-97a7-4470-a39b-f182d6fe8db0"}}
