{"type":"message","id":"934d4fc0","parentId":"a33982b6","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:15:15.949Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me add more pages for the other missing items.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7863c7a9d7a99e50c9afe394b27c","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Contradictions\ntype: process\nstatus: draft\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [contradiction, claims, synthesis]\n---\n\n# ⚔️ Contradictions\n\n> 矛盾与Claim 管理\n\n## 矛盾类型\n\n| 类型 | 描述 | 处理方式 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| **事实冲突** | A 说 X，B 说非 X | 保留双方，标注日期和来源 |\n| **过时信息** | 新数据 vs 旧结论 | 标记过时，保留参考 |\n| **观点差异** | 不同角度的分析 | 并存，注明立场 |\n\n## 标记格式\n\n```markdown\n### 矛盾记录\n\n| 日期 | 来源A | 来源B | 状态 |\n|------|-------|-------|------|\n| 2026-04-11 | 旧假设 | 新发现 | 待确认 |\n\n> [假设前提] 旧假设基于 X 条件...\n```\n\n## Claim 强度\n\n| 标记 | 含义 |\n|------|------|\n| 🟢 确认 | 有明确来源支持 |\n| 🟡 推测 | 有限证据 |\n| 🔴 存疑 | 与其他信息矛盾 |\n\n---\n\n## 执行时机\n\n- Ingest 新 source 时\n- 每周 Lint 时\n- 用户提问涉及已存在内容时\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[lint]] — 健康检查\n- [[ingest]] — 摄取流程\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/contradictions.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":5621,"output":374,"cacheRead":48256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54251,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775841298253,"responseId":"019d7863bd92a17150f27bc1fc2b6485"}}
