{"type":"message","id":"c00c3d3b","parentId":"e7c69336","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:16:09.358Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now update lint to be more specific about weekly maintenance.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7863d70202b1cd4bbfc8e60c55d3","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Lint\ntype: process\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [lint, health-check, wiki-maintenance]\n---\n\n# 🔍 Lint 工作流\n\n> Wiki 健康检查流程\n\n## 触发条件\n\n| 场景 | 频率 |\n|------|------|\n| 每次修改后 | 死链检查 |\n| 每周 | 全面检查 |\n| 实体页数量逢 10 | 全面检查 |\n| 重大变更后 | 手动 |\n\n---\n\n## 每周维护清单 (30分钟)\n\n### 1. 死链检查 (5分钟)\n\n```bash\ngrep -roh '\\[\\[[^]]*\\]\\]' memory/entities/*.md\n# 验证每个链接对应文件存在\n```\n\n### 2. 矛盾扫描 (10分钟)\n\n- 读取近期 Ingest 的页面\n- 与旧页面对比是否冲突\n- 标记: [[contradictions]]\n\n### 3. 过时检查 (5分钟)\n\n- 检查 last_updated > 30天 的页面\n- 判定是否仍有效\n- 标记 stale 或更新\n\n### 4. 孤儿检测 (5分钟)\n\n- 无任何页面链接到的页面\n- 添加相关链接或归档\n\n### 5. 缺失检测 (5分钟)\n\n- 提及但无页面的概念\n- 建议创建\n\n---\n\n## 输出格式\n\n```markdown\n## 🔍 Lint 报告 (2026-04-11)\n\n### 死链: 0 ✅\n### 矛盾: 1 🟡\n  - pageA vs pageB (待确认)\n### 过时: 2 ⚠️\n  - old-feature.md\n### 孤儿: 1\n  - unused.md\n### 缺失建议: 3 💡\n  - 建议创建 \"xxx\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 自动 vs 手动\n\n| 项目 | 自动 | 手动 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 死链检查 | ✅ | |\n| 时间戳检查 | ✅ | |\n| 矛盾识别 | | ✅ (需判断) |\n| 孤儿检测 | | ✅ |\n| 价值判断 | | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[memory]] — 记忆系统\n- [[ingest]] — 摄取流程\n- [[contradictions]] — 矛盾管理\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/lint.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":523,"output":557,"cacheRead":54784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55864,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775841343522,"responseId":"019d7863cd8e095b3f456ea1ea077e9f"}}
