{"type":"message","id":"a19ccd3c","parentId":"cb80cda7","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:16:58.745Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我继续思考。让我再深入对照 LLM Wiki 原文，看还有没有遗漏的关键点。\n\n原文中的关键点再检查：\n1. \"personal\" - 追踪自己的目标、健康、心理 - 无专属页\n2. \"research\" - 研究场景 - 无\n3. \"reading a book\" - 读书场景 - 无\n4. \"business/team\" - 团队 wiki - 无\n5. competitive analysis, due diligence, trip planning, course notes - 无\n6. \"Download images locally\" - 提到了但在 obsidian.md 不够详细\n7. \"graph view\" - 提到了不够详细\n8. \"Dataview\" - 提到了不够详细\n9. \"The wiki is just a git repo\" - 可以更强调整这个价值\n\n让我继续补全。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_83b3ba0763034f5d9966e8fd","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"book reading tracking personal goals health psychology","maxResults":3}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":55717,"output":209,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55926,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775841414937,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7ee45629-22e3-4c4c-a4b8-14972eca8bc6"}}
