{"type":"message","id":"03e189da","parentId":"7dc5dc8d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:17:52.221Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"创建 book wiki。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d78657d13c318012b89b6512a0e43","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Book Wiki\ntype: concept\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [book, reading, characters, themes]\n---\n\n# 📖 Book Wiki\n\n> 读书知识库\n\n## 适用场景\n\n- 读一本书时，边读边记\n- 按章节记录要点\n- 构建角色、主题、情节的关联\n- 读完后拥有完整的伴读 wiki\n\n## 类似案例\n\n[Tolkien Gateway](https://tolkiengateway.net) — 粉丝维护的托尔金百科\n- 数千个互关联的页面\n- 角色、地点、事件、语言\n\n## 页面结构\n\n```\nbook-书名/\n├── index.md         # 书籍概览\n├── chapter-1.md     # 第 N 章笔记\n├── chapter-2.md\n├── characters.md    # 角色列表\n├── places.md        # 地点\n├── themes.md        # 主题分析\n├── plot.md          # 情节线\n└── timeline.md      # 时间线\n```\n\n## 记录原则\n\n| 内容 | 记录方式 |\n|------|----------|\n| 章节要点 | 每章一文件 |\n| 新角色 | 创建独立页面 |\n| 伏笔 | 链接到后续章节 |\n| 主题 | 独立概念页 |\n\n## 与普通 wiki 的区别\n\n| 维度 | 普通 Wiki | Book Wiki |\n|------|-----------|-----------|\n| 时间 | 持续 | 读书周期 |\n| 结构 | 按概念 | 按章节+角色 |\n| 完整性 | 逐步完善 | 读完后完整 |\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[llm-wiki]] — 模式概念\n- [[human-role]] — 人的职责\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/book-wiki.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":4840,"output":422,"cacheRead":52224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57486,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775841446100,"responseId":"019d786573a04360a7183a662c49de39"}}
