{"type":"message","id":"64cc6658","parentId":"f2771bee","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:19:17.835Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"基于自身情况\"，意思是让我的分析是基于当前 OpenClaw 助手这个角色和现有工作区的实际情况，而不是泛泛而谈。\n\n让我想想对于一个 AI 助手来说，什么wiki场景是实际的：\n\n1. **Personal** - 小八(用户)可以用 Personal Wiki，但我(AI)主要是帮助维护系统\n2. **Research** - 可以用来做深度技术研究，比如深入学习一个框架\n3. **Book** - 可以用来记录读过的技术书籍\n4. **Team** - 目前没有团队协作需求\n5. 当前最实际的是：\n   - 技术学习 wiki (类似 Research)\n   - 项目 wiki (OpenClaw 相关)\n   - 技能学习 wiki (如 Claude Code)\n\n让我分析哪些对当前最实用，并给出建议。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7867b17b0cbbe23b073c8dad4311","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/ | wc -l"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":4559,"output":202,"cacheRead":55680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60441,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775841545904,"responseId":"019d78678bc60c687720bcddf366a2c4"}}
