{"type":"message","id":"b2d7d736","parentId":"e5612385","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:19:33.617Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求\"基于自身情况\"，意思是结合当前 OpenClaw + 我的角色（AI 助手）+ 工作区的实际情况。我来筛选最实用的场景。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n对照现有资产，筛选最实用的：\n\n## 实用场景筛选\n\n| 场景 | 实用性 | 原因 |\n|------|--------|------|\n| **Research Wiki** | ⭐⭐⭐ | 学习 Claude Code、OpenClaw 源码 |\n| **Book Wiki** | ⭐⭐ | 技术书籍笔记 |\n| **Team Wiki** | ⭐ | 暂无团队 |\n| **Personal Wiki** | ⭐ | 用户个人用，不是我维护 |\n\n**当前最实用**：\n\n1. **技术 Research** — 深入学习 Claude Code、OpenClaw 架构\n2. **Book Wiki** — 读技术书籍时记录\n\n要我创建这两个的具体示例吗？比如：\n- `research-claude-code/` 目录\n- `research-openclaw/` 目录"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":4780,"output":193,"cacheRead":55680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60653,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775841557914,"responseId":"019d7867b05a5de89f28fd74c4a174db"}}
