{"type":"message","id":"e6c9816f","parentId":"a74f1b63","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:20:39.219Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在创建一个\"错误知识库\"或\"纠正记录\"。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7868af0a7aee397c34e8fa4f959b","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Corrections\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [corrections, errors, learnings]\n---\n\n# ⚠️ Corrections\n\n> 错误与纠正记录\n\n## 概述\n\n用户的每一次纠正都是学习机会。\n\n| 规则 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 每次纠正 | 立即写入 ~/self-improving/corrections.md |\n| 分析根因 | 为什么错？ |\n| 避免重复 | 更新认知 |\n\n---\n\n## 格式\n\n```markdown\n## [2026-04-11] 纠正内容\n\n### 错误\n...我之前说/做了什么...\n\n### 正确\n...应该是...\n\n### 根因\n- 假设了错误的前提\n- 遗漏了关键信息\n\n### 改进\n- 以后遇到 X 场景要 Y\n```\n\n---\n\n## 历史记录\n\n已整合到 `~/self-improving/corrections.md`\n\n---\n\n## 常见错误类型\n\n| 类型 | 示例 |\n|------|------|\n| 臆造事实 | 说错了 API 版本 |\n| 忽略前提 | 没看清用户条件 |\n| 过度假设 | 自动脑补不存在的内容 |\n| 记忆偏差 | 记错了之前对话内容 |\n\n---\n\n## 避免策略\n\n1. 不确定 → 说\"不确定\"\n2. 引用 → 给出验证方法\n3. 假设 → 标注 `[假设前提]`\n4. 记住 → 立即写入文件\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[self-improving]] — 自我改进系统\n- [[memory]] — 记忆系统\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/corrections.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":897,"output":402,"cacheRead":60160,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61459,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775841619996,"responseId":"019d7868a65a86c86d42030857d7b467"}}
