{"type":"message","id":"c8076f67","parentId":"98c2c312","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:21:07.917Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在创建一个\"技能学习\"记录。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d78686f68aa43b7625aaa93df1b9e","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Skill Learnings\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [skill-learning, capability, growth]\n---\n\n# 📚 Skill Learnings\n\n> 技能学习与能力进化\n\n## 概述\n\n记录我学会了什么新技能、新工具、新工作流。\n\n---\n\n## 学习流程\n\n```\n1. 用户教会 / 发现新技能\n      ↓\n2. 理解原理\n      ↓\n3. 创建/更新 skill 页面\n      ↓\n4. 记录到 self-improving/\n      ↓\n5. 实践中应用\n```\n\n---\n\n## 已学习技能类型\n\n| 类别 | 示例 |\n|------|------|\n| 工具类 | Claude Code, obsidian, qmd |\n| 模式类 | LLM Wiki, TDD, Spec-first |\n| 工作流 | Ingest, Lint, Query Write-back |\n\n---\n\n## 技能成熟度\n\n| 等级 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 🟢 掌握 | 能独立执行 |\n| 🟡 学习中 | 需要用户确认 |\n| 🔴 新学 | 还不确定 |\n\n---\n\n## 记录位置\n\n- 详细记录: `~/self-improving/`\n- 技能索引: `entities/skills.md`\n- 经验总结: `entities/ai-research.md`\n\n---\n\n## 目标\n\n- 掌握 LLM Wiki 模式的完整工作流\n- 熟练使用 Obsidian + Dataview\n- 建立错误预防机制\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[skills]] — 技能清单\n- [[ai-research]] — AI 研究\n- [[self-improving]] — 自我改进\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/skill-learnings.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1341,"output":416,"cacheRead":60160,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61917,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775841639287,"responseId":"019d786866159a84f9c9abea70be4f99"}}
