{"type":"message","id":"70574d79","parentId":"a889a5ca","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:21:20.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"34 个了。汇报给用户。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n完成。基于我（AI）自身情况创建：\n\n| 实体页 | 用途 |\n|--------|------|\n| `ai-research.md` | 我的学习与进化记录 |\n| `corrections.md` | 错误与纠正知识库 |\n| `skill-learnings.md` | 技能学习与能力进化 |\n\n这些会让我：\n\n1. **记住学过什么** — 不再重复问同样的问题\n2. **记住犯过什么错** — 避免重复犯错\n3. **记住用户纠正** — 逐步适应用户风格\n4. **持续进化** — 从每次交互中学习\n\n**当前总数：34 个实体页**\n\n要继续补充，还是歇会？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":597,"output":153,"cacheRead":61440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62190,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775841672936,"responseId":"019d78697be8c696a52230638a5be482"}}
