{"type":"message","id":"bf744793","parentId":"173587fb","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:22:53.609Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续创建其他遗漏的页面。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_468773a70e66464eb8583740","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Batch Ingest\ntype: process\nstatus: draft\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [batch, ingest, efficiency]\n---\n\n# 📦 Batch Ingest\n\n> 批量摄取多个 Source\n\n## 场景\n\n| 场景 | 适用 |\n|------|------|\n| 收集了 10+ 篇文章 | 批量 Ingest |\n| 导入旧笔记 | 批量处理 |\n| 项目启动 | 快速建立知识库 |\n\n---\n\n## 工作流\n\n```\n1. 准备 sources\n   - 放入 raw/articles/ 或 raw/notes/\n   - 命名格式: YYYY-MM-标题.md\n\n2. 批量处理\n   - 一次读取多个文件\n   - 识别共性主题\n\n3. 批量输出\n   - 创建主索引页\n   - 创建各 source 摘要页\n   - 更新相关实体页 (可能 15-30 个)\n\n4. 验证\n   - 检查死链\n   - 检查重复\n```\n\n---\n\n## 批量 vs 单个\n\n| 维度 | 单个 Ingest | 批量 Ingest |\n|------|-------------|-------------|\n| 数量 | 1 个 | 10+ 个 |\n| 监督 | 高 (逐个确认) | 低 (自动化) |\n| 质量 | 高 | 中 |\n| 时间 | 长 | 短 |\n\n---\n\n## 建议\n\n- **初期**: 少量多次，保持参与\n- **熟悉后**: 可以批量，但定期回顾质量\n- **任何时候**: 定期 lint 检查一致性\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[ingest]] — 单个摄取流程\n- [[raw-sources]] — 源文件管理\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/batch-ingest.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":63115,"output":423,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63538,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775841767188,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a8ca8c6a-a9bb-43e8-b955-028d46d93383"}}
