{"type":"message","id":"2c072b14","parentId":"b42b973e","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:23:14.289Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续创建其他页面。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d786a489aadad16b74c57770cbffe","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Quick Start\ntype: process\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [quick-start, onboarding, review]\n---\n\n# 🚀 Quick Start\n\n> 快速了解 Wiki 状态\n\n## 首次了解一个 Wiki\n\n```bash\n# 1. 看 index (5分钟)\ncat MEMORY.md\n\n# 2. 看最近更新 (2分钟)\ngrep \"last_updated\" memory/entities/*.md | tail -10\n\n# 3. 看 graph (5分钟)\n# Obsidian: Ctrl+G 查看\n\n# 4. 运行 lint (10分钟)\n# 检查健康状态\n```\n\n## 快速检查清单\n\n| 时间 | 检查项 | 命令 |\n|------|--------|------|\n| 1分钟 | 实体页数量 | `ls entities/ | wc -l` |\n| 2分钟 | 最近更新 | `grep -h \"last_updated\" entities/*.md | tail -5` |\n| 3分钟 | 死链检查 | `grep -roh '\\[\\[.*\\]\\]' entities/` |\n| 5分钟 | Graph View | Obsidian Ctrl+G |\n\n---\n\n## 快速了解一个主题\n\n```bash\n# 搜索关键词\nopenclaw memory search \"主题\"\n\n# 直接看相关页面\ncat entities/主题.md\n\n# 看这个主题关联了哪些\ngrep -l \"主题\" entities/*.md\n```\n\n---\n\n## 新手建议\n\n1. **先看**: second-brain-report.md\n2. **再看**: wiki-schema.md\n3. **再读**: llm-wiki.md\n4. **实操**: 尝试一次 Ingest\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[second-brain-report]] — 构建报告\n- [[search]] — 搜索工具\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/quick-start.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3158,"output":431,"cacheRead":60416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64005,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775841773668,"responseId":"019d786a3fd4e001b630a9c73b757535"}}
