{"type":"message","id":"7c8b04c1","parentId":"9614aed3","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:24:49.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好了，完成深度思考补充。让我给用户一个总结。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n深度补全完成。\n\n## 新增 6 个深层页面\n\n| 页面 | 补全点 |\n|------|--------|\n| `query-workflow.md` | 强化\"问答也让 wiki 丰富\" |\n| `batch-ingest.md` | 批量处理多个 source |\n| `quick-start.md` | 如何快速了解 wiki 状态 |\n| `migration.md` | 从 Notion/Obsidian 等迁移 |\n| `why-wiki.md` | 成本/收益分析 |\n| `privacy-security.md` | 敏感信息处理 |\n\n## 同步更新\n\n- `ai-research.md`, `corrections.md`, `skill-learnings.md` — AI 自身学习\n\n## 最终统计\n\n**40 个实体页**\n\n| 类别 | 数量 |\n|------|------|\n| 核心系统 | 10 |\n| LLM Wiki 模式 | 8 |\n| 工作流 | 8 |\n| 场景应用 | 6 |\n| AI 自身 | 3 |\n| 工具/其他 | 5 |\n\n完整对齐 LLM Wiki 原文。可以歇了 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":66233,"output":242,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66475,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775841885871,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9cc57026-8352-49cd-a290-eb79ca31de47"}}
