{"type":"message","id":"53a31c58","parentId":"f2484bd6","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:26:01.088Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问我是否还记得需求和原文。让我回顾一下：\n\n1. 用户最初给了 LLM Wiki 的原文\n2. 用户让我\"全面认真学习，进行思考，基于自身情况\"\n3. 我做了深度分析并创建了大量实体页\n\n现在用户问我是否记得原文内容和需求。让我搜索一下 memory 看是否有记录，或者直接回答我记得的核心内容。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n记得。\n\n## 需求\n\n> **全面认真学习，进行思考，基于自身情况：LLM Wiki**\n\n核心要求：\n1. 学习 LLM Wiki 模式\n2. 结合我自身情况\n3. 认真思考，不是敷衍\n\n## 原文核心要点\n\n| 核心 | 原文关键句 |\n|------|-----------|\n| **不是 RAG** | \"Instead of just retrieving... the LLM incrementally builds and maintains a persistent wiki\" |\n| **编译 vs 重新发现** | \"knowledge is compiled once and then kept current\" |\n| **维护成本归零** | \"LLMs don't get bored, don't forget to update a cross-reference\" |\n| **人之职责** | \"The human's job is to curate sources, direct the analysis, ask good questions\" |\n| **双屏工作流** | \"LLM on one side and Obsidian on the other\" |\n| **Memex 呼应** | \"The part he couldn't solve was who does the maintenance. The LLM handles that.\" |\n\n## 我的实践对照\n\n| 原文 | 我做了什么 |\n|------|------------|\n| 实体页 | ✅ 40 个实体页 |\n| Raw Sources | ✅ 创建 raw/ 目录 + raw-sources.md |\n| Ingest 流程 | ✅ 定义完整 + 自动扩散 |\n| Query Write-back | ✅ query-workflow.md |\n| Lint 机制 | ✅ 每周维护清单 |\n| Obsidian | ✅ 配置详解 |\n| 输出格式 | ✅ output-formats.md |\n| 人之职责 | ✅ human-role.md |\n| 隐私/安全 | ✅ privacy-security.md |\n| 成本/收益 | ✅ why-wiki.md |\n\n**已完成闭环** 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":4070,"output":421,"cacheRead":62080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66571,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775841939878,"responseId":"019d786cc943ef1c3e3a180a2e05a439"}}
