{"type":"message","id":"038fe1cc","parentId":"176b45c0","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:26:38.917Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我继续深入思考。让我再想想还有什么是原文提到但我没有真正落实的，或者可以进一步改进的地方。\n\n让我再想想：\n1. 原文强调的是\"持续维护\"而不是一次性工作\n2. 双屏工作流的具体实践\n3. 知识的具体来源 - 不仅仅是概念，还要有实际的输入\n4. 我作为 AI 如何真正使用这个 wiki\n5. 下一步是什么 - 不是做完就算，而是真正用起来\n\n让我思考\"用起来\"这个点。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d786da80be262efc38664582f16d6","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"practical usage workflow experience improvement","maxResults":3}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":4480,"output":141,"cacheRead":62080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66701,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775841989130,"responseId":"019d786d89913b0a396d8f98cb0adacc"}}
