{"type":"message","id":"389ce3c0","parentId":"c56f97ed","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:27:59.798Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我给出最终总结，告诉用户这是实际可以用的了。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n完成。\n\n## 新增落地页\n\n| 页面 | 解决什么问题 |\n|------|--------------|\n| `knowledge-sources.md` | Wiki 吃什么——知识从哪里来 |\n| `ai-usage.md` | 我(AI)怎么用 wiki 回答问题 |\n| `user-access.md` | 用户怎么查看 wiki |\n| `wiki-evolution.md` | wiki 自身怎么迭代 |\n\n## 关键闭环\n\n```\n知识来源 → AI 读取 → 写入 Wiki → 回答用户 → 持续迭代\n```\n\n## 现在是实际可用的系统\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 44 个实体页 | ✅ |\n| Schema 规范 | ✅ |\n| Ingest 流程 | ✅ |\n| Query 写回 | ✅ |\n| AI 使用流程 | ✅ |\n| 用户访问方式 | ✅ |\n| 迭代计划 | ✅ |\n\n**可以开始用了** 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":69287,"output":204,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69491,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775842076160,"responseId":"chatcmpl-efbdb88f-220f-47e8-9bf2-1d049265dfbb"}}
