{"type":"message","id":"e9a5aa69","parentId":"139972bc","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:31:00.233Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Let me provide a summary.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n完成。\n\n## 新增实用页\n\n| 页面 | 解决什么问题 |\n|------|--------------|\n| `wiki-prompts.md` | 用户怎么命令我操作 wiki |\n| `system-integration.md` | Wiki 和 AGENTS.md/SOUL.md 关系 |\n| `edge-cases.md` | Wiki 处理不了的边界情况 |\n| `wiki-metrics.md` | 怎么衡量 wiki 健康 |\n| `backup-strategy.md` | 丢了怎么办 |\n\n## 关键补全\n\n- **Prompt 模板** — 从自然语言到具体指令\n- **系统整合** — Wiki 在现有系统中的位置\n- **边界情况** — 新领域/不确定/敏感信息处理\n- **监控指标** — 量化健康度\n- **备份恢复** — Git + 手动双重保护\n\n## 最终统计\n\n**49 个实体页**\n\n从 LLM Wiki 理论 → 实际落地完整闭环。\n\n还要继续吗 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":73040,"output":208,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73248,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775842256676,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c810e91f-6cc1-4457-be50-a9e41ed96a5e"}}
