{"type":"message","id":"99b8aa2c","parentId":"76022d14","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:32:25.419Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我继续思考更多方面。每一轮我会增加几个有价值的实体页。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 第 1-2 轮：进阶实践\n\n| 维度 | 缺失 | 动作 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **模板** | 创建新页的模板 | 新增 |\n| **命名规范** | 具体命名规则细化 | 新增 |\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d787365d55e2efa77b4bcd199e9e8","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Page Templates\ntype: process\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [templates, starting-point, boilerplate]\n---\n\n# 📋 Page Templates\n\n> 创建新页面模板\n\n## Entity 模板\n\n```markdown\n---\ntitle: {标题}\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: {YYYY-MM-DD}\ntags: [{标签1}, {标签2}]\n---\n\n# {emoji} {标题}\n\n> 一句话描述\n\n## 概览\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| ... | ... |\n\n## 核心内容\n\n...\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[entity]] — 描述\n```\n\n## Concept 模板\n\n```markdown\n---\ntitle: {概念}\ntype: concept\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: {YYYY-MM-DD}\ntags: [{标签}]\n---\n\n# 💡 {概念}\n\n> 一句话定义\n\n## 核心理念\n\n...\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[related]] — 相关概念\n```\n\n## Process 模板\n\n```markdown\n---\ntitle: {流程名}\ntype: process\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: {YYYY-MM-DD}\ntags: [{标签}]\n---\n\n# 📥 {流程名}\n\n> 流程描述\n\n## 触发条件\n\n| 场景 | 处理 |\n|------|------|\n| ... | ... |\n\n## 操作步骤\n\n```\n1. 步骤一\n2. 步骤二\n3. 步骤三\n```\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[related]]\n```\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[wiki-schema]] — Schema 规范\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/page-templates.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3958,"output":458,"cacheRead":69248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73664,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775842318315,"responseId":"019d78734abe33637d233bf992b66d5e"}}
