{"type":"message","id":"965e7e22","parentId":"c97fe7ea","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:33:11.382Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续深度思考。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d78743108e1053a360be91a7985c3","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Version History\ntype: process\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [git, history, rollback]\n---\n\n# 📜 Version History\n\n> Git 版本历史使用\n\n## 查看历史\n\n```bash\n# 看修改历史\ncd memory\ngit log --oneline -20\n\n# 看某个文件的修改\ngit log --oneline entities/openclaw.md\n\n# 看具体变化\ngit diff HEAD~5 entities/openclaw.md\n```\n\n---\n\n## 恢复场景\n\n| 场景 | 命令 |\n|------|------|\n| 误删页面 | `git checkout HEAD~1 -- entities/deleted.md` |\n| 改错了 | `git checkout HEAD -- entities/xxx.md` |\n| 想看旧版 | `git show HEAD~3:entities/xxx.md > /tmp/old.md` |\n\n---\n\n## 版本标注\n\n每次重要更新添加有意义的 commit：\n\n```bash\n# 好\ngit commit -m \"feat: add query-workflow, improve ingest\"\n\n# 不好\ngit commit -m \"update\"\ngit commit -m \"changes\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 分支实验\n\n```bash\n# 创建实验分支\ngit checkout -b experiment/new-structure\n\n# 实验成功合并\ngit checkout main\ngit merge experiment/new-structure\n\n# 实验失败删除\ngit branch -d experiment/new-structure\n```\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[git]] — 版本控制\n- [[backup-strategy]] — 备份策略\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/version-history.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":5459,"output":371,"cacheRead":69248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75078,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775842373765,"responseId":"019d787427324f5f183431180b6eb523"}}
