{"type":"message","id":"03707805","parentId":"b1b2b22c","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:34:47.715Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续深入思考。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n\n\n## 第 9-10 轮：实际案例\n\n| 维度 | 缺失 | 动作 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **使用案例** | 具体怎么用 | 新增 |\n| **失败模式** | 常见失败原因 | 新增 |\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7874e110d3a3988f38efb8870fcd","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Use Cases\ntype: concept\nstatus: reference\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [use-cases, examples, scenarios]\n---\n\n# 🎯 Use Cases\n\n> Wiki 实际使用案例\n\n## 案例1: 学新技术\n\n```\n用户: \"帮我看看 Claude Code 的 tools 实现\"\n我:\n  1. 搜索 wiki: \"claude-code tools\"\n  2. 读取 entities/claude-code.md\n  3. 综合回答\n  4. 如果用户补充了新理解 → 写回 wiki\n```\n\n## 案例2: 记录偏好\n\n```\n用户: \"我喜欢简洁的回答\"\n我:\n  1. 确认 \"记住这个偏好\"\n  2. 更新 entities/preferences.md\n  3. 未来自动使用这个偏好\n```\n\n## 案例3: 深度研究\n\n```\n用户: \"我想深入了解 LLM Wiki 模式\"\n我:\n  1. 读取 entities/llm-wiki.md\n  2. 读取 entities/ingest.md, entities/lint.md 等相关页\n  3. 综合整理\n  4. 如果有新的理解 → 建议写回\n```\n\n## 案例4: 错误复盘\n\n```\n用户: \"你之前那个说法不对\"\n我:\n  1. 承认错误\n  2. 写入 entities/corrections.md\n  3. 如果影响已有 wiki 内容 → 更新\n```\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[ai-usage]] — 使用流程\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/use-cases.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1119,"output":446,"cacheRead":75776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77341,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775842465639,"responseId":"019d7874cf2f423d1c3a3813467284a7"}}
