{"type":"message","id":"7ae367d0","parentId":"b1a8fbcf","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:34:54.288Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续思考更多内容。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ab5f93df8ba44e13a1380911","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Failure Modes\ntype: concept\nstatus: reference\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [failure, problems, pitfalls]\n---\n\n# 💥 Failure Modes\n\n> 常见失败模式与避免\n\n## Wiki 失败原因\n\n| 失败模式 | 原因 | 解决方案 |\n|----------|------|----------|\n| **建了不用** | 热情消退 | 融入日常使用 |\n| **过于复杂** | Schema 太严格 | 简化，从简单开始 |\n| **质量下降** | 什么 都往里记 | 只记有价值的 |\n| **维护真空** | 不 Lint | 定期维护 |\n| **孤岛效应** | 页面不链接 | 强制链接 |\n\n---\n\n## 避免策略\n\n### 1. 持续使用\n\n```\n- 每次重要对话后考虑写回\n- 定期 lint 保持健康\n- 周期性回顾\n```\n\n### 2. 质量控制\n\n```\n- 不是所有都要写\n- 有洞见才写回\n- 定期清理过时内容\n```\n\n### 3. 简单开始\n\n```\n- 先有一页\n- 再慢慢扩展\n- 不要追求完美Schema\n```\n\n---\n\n## 成功标志\n\n| 标志 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 能回答之前的问题 | 积累有效 |\n| 链接在生长 | 知识互联 |\n| 定期有更新 | 活跃维护 |\n| 检索有结果 | 真正有用 |\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[wiki-mindset]] — 心态\n- [[wiki-evolution]] — 迭代\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/failure-modes.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":77419,"output":399,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77818,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775842487802,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8a2c38e8-eec0-4a26-a5ef-c1a6a356adb2"}}
