{"type":"message","id":"4dd6dae0","parentId":"b6b2f6dd","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:35:31.472Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续思考更多内容。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7c81f5adce4d46e2abf4af06","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Scheduled Tasks\ntype: process\nstatus: draft\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [cron, schedule, automation]\n---\n\n# ⏰ Scheduled Tasks\n\n> 定时自动任务\n\n## Wiki 维护任务\n\n| 任务 | 频率 | 命令 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 死链检查 | 每次修改后 | `grep -roh '\\[\\['` |\n| Lint | 每周 | 手动执行 |\n| 备份 | 每天 | Git push |\n| 清理临时文件 | 每周 | `rm memory/ephemeral/*` |\n\n---\n\n## Cron 示例\n\n```bash\n# 每天凌晨 2 点自动备份\n0 2 * * * cd ~/memory && git add . && git commit -m \"backup $(date +%Y-%m-%d)\" && git push\n\n# 每周日凌晨运行 lint\n0 3 * * 0 cd ~/memory && ./scripts/lint.sh >> logs/lint.log\n```\n\n---\n\n## OpenClaw Cron\n\n使用 OpenClaw 自带的 cron：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw cron add \\\n  --schedule \"0 2 * * *\" \\\n  --command \"cd memory && git add . && git commit -m 'backup' && git push\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[backup-strategy]] — 备份策略\n- [[lint]] — 健康检查\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/scheduled-tasks.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":78297,"output":361,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78658,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775842525603,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b818ef0d-3c5b-49d1-8720-ba09bb4ce3fd"}}
