{"type":"message","id":"1c646c0b","parentId":"90e4f80e","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:35:57.689Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续思考更多内容。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d78761a0caf9f4460543f9e2aa559","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Knowledge Graph\ntype: concept\nstatus: reference\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [graph, visualization, relation]\n---\n\n# 🕸️ Knowledge Graph\n\n> 知识图谱可视化\n\n## Obsidian Graph View\n\n快捷键: Ctrl+G\n\n### 功能\n- 节点: 页面\n- 边: 链接 [[]]\n- 颜色: 标签\n- 大小: 入链数\n\n---\n\n## 分析技巧\n\n### 找 Hub 页面\n\nHub = 链接到很多其他页面的页面\n\n```bash\n# 找链接最多的页面\nfor f in *.md; do\n  count=$(grep -c '\\[\\[' $f)\n  echo \"$count $f\"\ndone | sort -rn | head -5\n```\n\n### 找孤儿页面\n\n```bash\n# 没有链接到它的页面\nfor f in *.md; do\n  page=$(basename $f .md)\n  grep -q \"\\[\\[$page\\]\\]\" *.md || echo \"$page\"\ndone\n```\n\n---\n\n## Graph 优化\n\n| 问题 | 解决 |\n|------|------|\n| 太乱 | 过滤特定 tag |\n| 孤儿多 | 添加链接 |\n| 找不到中心 | 突出 Hub 页面 |\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[obsidian]] — IDE\n- [[lint]] — 健康检查\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/knowledge-graph.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":4596,"output":353,"cacheRead":74624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79573,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775842540089,"responseId":"019d7876101c47484bf81740020416f4"}}
