{"type":"message","id":"954c0e6d","parentId":"016a674e","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:36:43.699Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续思考更多内容。\n\n第17-18轮：发布和分享相关\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7876bea053f66f4491eaf1fa752d","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Sharing\ntype: concept\nstatus: reference\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [sharing, publishing, public]\n---\n\n# 📤 Sharing\n\n> Wiki 发布与分享\n\n## 分享方式\n\n| 方式 | 说明 | 隐私 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 导出 MD | 直接给文件 | 取决于内容 |\n| GitHub 公开仓库 | 公开代码/笔记 | 检查敏感信息 |\n| 部分页面 | 只分享特定页面 | 完全可控 |\n| 静态网站 | 用 Obsidian Publish | 可选择公开内容 |\n\n---\n\n## 导出命令\n\n```bash\n# 导出全部\ncp -r memory/entities/ /tmp/wiki-export/\n\n# 导出特定页面\ncat entities/openclaw.md | grep -v \"tags:.*private\" > /tmp/export.md\n\n# 导出为 PDF (需要 pandoc)\npandoc entities/openclaw.md -o openclaw.pdf\n```\n\n---\n\n## 静态网站\n\n### Obsidian Publish\n\n```bash\n# Obsidian 内置\n# Settings → Publish → 选择页面 → 发布\n```\n\n### 其他方案\n\n| 方案 | 特点 |\n|------|------|\n| VitePress | Vue 静态站 |\n| Docusaurus | React 静态站 |\n| MkDocs | Python 静态站 |\n\n---\n\n## 隐私检查\n\n分享前：\n\n```bash\n# 检查敏感词\ngrep -r \"password\\|secret\\|key\\|token\" memory/entities/ || echo \"✅ 无敏感信息\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[privacy-security]] — 隐私安全\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/sharing.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":604,"output":409,"cacheRead":79488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80501,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775842582313,"responseId":"019d7876b50626f8acf3c22d5f06b06a"}}
