{"type":"message","id":"a200bfdb","parentId":"1cfb9610","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:37:15.501Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续思考更多内容。\n\n第19-20轮：最后两个重要的主题\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bc9296752853401bb2d09325","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Knowledge Reuse\ntype: concept\nstatus: reference\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [reuse, recombination, synthesis]\n---\n\n# 🔄 Knowledge Reuse\n\n> 知识的复用与重组\n\n## 复用方式\n\n| 方式 | 说明 | 示例 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **直接引用** | 链接到已有页面 | 读取 [[entity]] |\n| **综合** | 合并多个来源 | 创建新页面 |\n| **对比** | 比较异同 | 创建对比表 |\n| **派生** | 从 A 推到 B | 推理新结论 |\n\n---\n\n## 复用流程\n\n```\n1. 遇到问题/主题 X\n      ↓\n2. 搜索 wiki 中相关页面\n      ↓\n3. 读取 2-3 个相关页\n      ↓\n4. 综合形成答案\n      ↓\n5. 判断是否写回:\n   - 是 → 创建/更新页面\n   - 否 → 直接回答\n```\n\n---\n\n## 复用的价值\n\n- **时间**: 不需要每次重新理解\n- **深度**: 跨领域连接产生新洞察\n- **质量**: 综合多个可靠来源\n\n---\n\n## 复用案例\n\n```\n用户: \"什么是 LLM Wiki?\"\n→ 读取 llm-wiki.md (基础)\n→ 读取 ingest.md (工作流)\n→ 读取 second-brain-report.md (实践)\n→ 综合成一个完整的回答\n→ 如果回答得好 → 写回 wiki\n```\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[query-workflow]] — 查询流程\n- [[output-formats]] — 输出格式\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/knowledge-reuse.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":81209,"output":414,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81623,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775842628911,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8169e0f7-ce18-42b8-b1de-cb895996b4f7"}}
