{"type":"message","id":"8a95cbac","parentId":"5938b40b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:47:55.545Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me continue with rounds 21-25 focusing on content quality and refinement.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 第 21-25 轮：内容质量与优化\n\n| 轮次 | 维度 | 动作 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 21 | 内容质量标准 | 新增 |\n| 22 | 页面合并与拆分 | 新增 |\n| 23 | 过时内容处理 | 新增 |\n| 24 | 内容迁移 | 新增 |\n| 25 | 质量审核标准 | 新增 |\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7881b4b22e04f24bbd7c5fbf00ea","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Content Quality\ntype: concept\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [quality, standards, content]\n---\n\n# ✨ Content Quality\n\n> Wiki 内容质量标准\n\n## 质量级别\n\n| 级别 | 说明 | 特征 |\n|------|------|------|\n| ⭐ 参考级 | 可靠、完整 | 有来源、结构清晰 |\n| 📝 记录级 | 有用但不完美 | 基础信息、有待完善 |\n| 🌱 草稿级 | 初始版本 | 只有框架、待填充 |\n| 🗑️ 待删 | 已过时/无用 | 应该删除 |\n\n---\n\n## 质量标准\n\n### 必须有\n\n- ✅ frontmatter (title, type, status, last_updated)\n- ✅ 至少一个相关链接\n- ✅ 有实际内容（非仅模板）\n\n### 最好有\n\n- 📝 tags\n- 📝 相关页面链接\n- 📝 代码示例（如果是技术类）\n\n### 不应该有\n\n- ❌ 死链\n- ❌ 完全空白\n- ❌ 重复内容\n\n---\n\n## 质量检查\n\n```bash\n# 检查缺失 frontmatter\nfor f in *.md; do\n  head -5 $f | grep -q \"title:\" || echo \"❌ $f 缺失 title\"\ndone\n\n# 检查空页面\nfind . -name \"*.md\" -empty -ls\n```\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[lint]] — 健康检查\n- [[review-process]] — 审查流程\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/content-quality.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":10041,"output":487,"cacheRead":72960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83488,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775843253107,"responseId":"019d7881997b96faef7d39659ac6a151"}}
