{"type":"message","id":"ebe023bb","parentId":"59f13bde","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:48:20.168Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Continue with round 22-25:\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d788170f2dc3f7c945c5d3c0bd036","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Page Split Merge\ntype: process\nstatus: draft\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [split, merge, refactoring]\n---\n\n# 🔀 Page Split & Merge\n\n> 页面拆分与合并\n\n## 何时拆分\n\n| 信号 | 操作 |\n|------|------|\n| 一个页面超过 500 行 | 拆分成多个 |\n| 内容涉及多个主题 | 按主题拆分 |\n| 页面太宽泛 | 拆成专业页面 |\n\n## 何时合并\n\n| 信号 | 操作 |\n|------|------|\n| 多个页面内容高度重复 | 合并 |\n| 相关页面但访问量都低 | 合并 |\n| 过细的分类 | 合并 |\n\n## 拆分步骤\n\n```\n1. 创建新页面 (按模板)\n2. 复制相关章节到新页\n3. 原页保留精简版 + 链接到新页\n4. 检查所有引用旧页的链接\n5. 更新 MEMORY.md\n```\n\n## 合并步骤\n\n```\n1. 选择主页面\n2. 从其他页面复制内容\n3. 删除被合并的页面\n4. 更新所有指向被删除页面的链接\n5. 更新 MEMORY.md\n```\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[content-quality]] — 质量标准\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/page-split-merge.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":10568,"output":339,"cacheRead":72960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83867,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775843275619,"responseId":"019d78815f344885f10ff2ba1ac2355c"}}
