{"type":"message","id":"9c7abd65","parentId":"aee31d32","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:49:04.499Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Round 25 - Quality audit criteria, then continue with rounds 26-30:\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d78821d319effbd6fd59396271134","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Quality Audit\ntype: process\nstatus: draft\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [audit, evaluation, assessment]\n---\n\n# 📋 Quality Audit\n\n> 质量审核标准\n\n## 审核维度\n\n| 维度 | 权重 | 检查项 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| 完整性 | 30% | 是否涵盖核心内容 |\n| 准确性 | 30% | 信息是否正确 |\n| 可读性 | 20% | 格式是否清晰 |\n| 链接 | 20% | 链接是否有效 |\n\n---\n\n## 评分标准\n\n| 分数 | 等级 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 90-100 | A | 优秀，直接可用 |\n| 70-89 | B | 良好，稍作修改 |\n| 50-69 | C | 一般，需要补充 |\n| <50 | D | 需要重构 |\n\n---\n\n## 审核流程\n\n```\n1. 随机抽取 10% 页面\n2. 按维度评分\n3. 汇总统计\n4. 制定改进计划\n5. 执行优化\n```\n\n---\n\n## 工具辅助\n\n```bash\n# 完整性检查\nwc -l *.md | awk '$1<50 {print}'\n\n# 链接检查\n./scripts/check-dead-links.sh\n```\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[content-quality]] — 质量标准\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/quality-audit.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":11725,"output":369,"cacheRead":72960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85054,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775843324747,"responseId":"019d788209c411fd4709cdbdc86a5333"}}
