{"type":"message","id":"ccf40a0b","parentId":"7c9d5852","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:50:00.763Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Round 28 - Macros and Scripts, round 29 - Backlinks, then round 30 - Log analysis:\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d78838f1d609d52bd22740152bb35","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Macros\ntype: process\nstatus: draft\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [macros, automation, scripts]\n---\n\n# 🧬 Macros\n\n> 自动化宏\n\n## 常用宏\n\n### 自动添加相关链接\n\n```python\n# auto-link.py\n# 为页面自动添加相关页面链接\n\nimport os\nimport re\n\ndef add_related_links(page):\n    with open(page) as f:\n        content = f.read()\n    \n    # 提取当前页面的关键词\n    words = re.findall(r'\\b[A-Z][a-z]+(?:\\s+[A-Z][a-z]+)*\\b', content)\n    \n    # 查找可链接的页面\n    for other in os.listdir('.'):\n        if other.endswith('.md') and other != page:\n            for word in words:\n                if word.lower() in other.lower():\n                    content += f\"\\n- [[{other[:-3]}]] (自动关联)\"\n    \n    with open(page, 'w') as f:\n        f.write(content)\n```\n\n### 自动更新目录\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# 自动更新 MEMORY.md 索引\necho \"| 页面 | 描述 |\" > temp.md\necho \"|------|------|\" >> temp.md\nfor f in *.md; do\n  title=$(head -1 $f | sed 's/# //')\n  echo \"| [$title]($f) | 自动 |\" >> temp.md\ndone\n```\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[automation-scripts]] — 脚本\n- [[page-templates]] — 模板\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/macros.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3069,"output":423,"cacheRead":82944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86436,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775843379727,"responseId":"019d788381724eb6a3bb1bbd01b52595"}}
