{"type":"message","id":"a2a548ad","parentId":"6fcf5f85","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:50:21.906Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Round 29 - Backlinks, round 30 - Log analysis:\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d78833c50fed67664e93ccbd96e41","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Backlinks\ntype: concept\nstatus: reference\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [backlinks, incoming-links, references]\n---\n\n# 🔙 Backlinks\n\n> 反向链接\n\n## 概念\n\n| 链接类型 | 说明 | 示例 |\n|----------|------|------|\n| 前向链接 | 从 A → B | A 页面链接到 B |\n| 反向链接 | B ← A | 链接到 B 的页面 |\n\n---\n\n## 查看反向链接\n\n### 命令行\n\n```bash\n# 找所有链接到某页面的链接\ngrep -roh '\\[\\[target-page\\]\\]' *.md | wc -l\n\n# 列出所有反向链接\nfor page in *.md; do\n  target=$(basename $page .md)\n  links=$(grep -c \"\\[\\[$target\\]\\]\" *.md)\n  if [ $links -gt 0 ]; then\n    echo \"$page: $links 个反向链接\"\n  fi\ndone\n```\n\n### Obsidian\n\n- 右键页面 → \"Show backlinks\"\n\n---\n\n## 反向链接的价值\n\n- 发现隐藏关联\n- 评估页面重要性 (入链数)\n- 找到孤儿页面\n\n---\n\n## 自动生成反向链接\n\n```python\n# 为每个页面生成反向链接章节\nfor page in *.md; do\n  name=$(basename $page .md)\n  echo -e \"\\n## 反向链接\\n\" >> $page\n  grep -l \"\\[\\[$name\\]\\]\" *.md | while read f; do\n    echo \"- [[$(basename $f .md)]]\" >> $page\n  done\ndone\n```\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[knowledge-graph]] — 知识图谱\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/backlinks.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1485,"output":440,"cacheRead":84992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86917,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775843400843,"responseId":"019d788332a5842fe4333a79aa13e3f2"}}
