{"type":"message","id":"9fdb5269","parentId":"53f36dca","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:52:02.497Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Round 35 - Learning notes, then continue with rounds 36-40 for technical details:\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7884cc94a964d31817a93b12df80","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Learning Notes\ntype: concept\nstatus: reference\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [learning, notes, study]\n---\n\n# 📖 Learning Notes\n\n> 学习笔记知识库\n\n## 适用场景\n\n- 课程笔记\n- 读书笔记\n- 教程学习\n- 认证考试\n\n---\n\n## 页面结构\n\n```\nlearning/\n├── course-name/      # 每门课程\n│   ├── week1.md\n│   ├── week2.md\n│   └── summary.md\n├── books/            # 书籍笔记\n├── tutorials/        # 教程\n└── exams/            # 考试准备\n```\n\n---\n\n## 笔记格式\n\n### 康奈尔笔记法\n\n```markdown\n# 主题\n\n## 线索\n[关键词/问题]\n\n## 笔记\n[主要内容和解释]\n\n## 总结\n[简短摘要]\n```\n\n### 详细笔记\n\n```markdown\n# [课程/书籍名称]\n\n## 核心概念\n1. 概念 A\n2. 概念 B\n\n## 详细解释\n...\n\n## 思考与问题\n...\n\n## 相关页面\n- [[related]]\n```\n\n---\n\n## 复用价值\n\n- 考试复习\n- 面试准备\n- 快速回顾\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[book-wiki]] — 读书笔记\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/learning-notes.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1668,"output":357,"cacheRead":87296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89321,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775843502899,"responseId":"019d7884c15add6da45d15eae0dbf6d0"}}
