{"type":"message","id":"a6703ed5","parentId":"47f03c7c","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:52:10.144Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now rounds 36-40 - Technical details:\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n\n## 第 36-40 轮：技术细节\n\n| 轮次 | 维度 | 动作 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 36 | 搜索优化 | 新增 |\n| 37 | 索引优化 | 新增 |\n| 38 | 性能优化 | 新增 |\n| 39 | 插件生态 | 新增 |\n| 40 | 数据结构 | 新增 |\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_25bd3d7aad3f4dbdb19f0592","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Search Optimization\ntype: process\nstatus: draft\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [search, optimization, performance]\n---\n\n# 🔍 Search Optimization\n\n> 搜索优化\n\n## 当前搜索方式\n\n| 工具 | 优点 | 缺点 |\n|------|------|------|\n| grep | 快速、简单 | 仅关键词 |\n| memory_search | 语义搜索 | 依赖外部 API |\n| qmd | 本地 + 语义 | 需安装 |\n\n---\n\n## 优化策略\n\n### 1. 文件命名\n\n```\n✅ descriptive-page-name.md\n❌ untitled.md\n✅ 2026-04-11-notes.md\n❌ notes.md\n```\n\n### 2. 内容结构\n\n```markdown\n# 一级标题 (重要关键词)\n## 二级标题 (长尾关键词)\n内容包含更多关键词...\n```\n\n### 3. 添加索引词\n\n```markdown\n---\ntitle: Docker\ntags: [docker, container, devops]\n---\n# 🐳 Docker\n\n关键词: 容器化, 镜像, Dockerfile, containerd\n```\n\n---\n\n## 搜索技巧\n\n```bash\n# 精确匹配\ngrep -w \"Docker\" *.md\n\n# 不区分大小写\ngrep -i \"docker\" *.md\n\n# 上下文\ngrep -C 3 \"关键词\" *.md\n\n# 正则\ngrep -E \"(Docker|Kubernetes)\" *.md\n```\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[search]] — 搜索工具\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/search-optimization.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":89430,"output":470,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89900,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775843522575,"responseId":"chatcmpl-6f47d52b-2ab4-437d-a045-6c1e39ade220"}}
