{"type":"message","id":"ce99b11d","parentId":"6533499d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:53:05.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Continue with more:\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1d9b04dce0484f00a3c8a3cd","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Navigation Design\ntype: concept\nstatus: reference\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [navigation, ux, layout]\n---\n\n# 🧭 Navigation Design\n\n> 导航设计\n\n## 导航层次\n\n### 1. 全局导航 (MEMORY.md)\n\n```\nMEMORY.md ← 顶层入口\n  ├── 核心系统\n  ├── LLM Wiki 模式\n  └── 工作流\n```\n\n### 2. 分类导航 (目录页)\n\n```\n目录页 ← 某类内容的索引\n  ├── 页面1\n  ├── 页面2\n  └── 页面3\n```\n\n### 3. 页面导航 (内容内)\n\n```\n页面内\n  ├── 目录 (Table of Contents)\n  ├── 顶部链接\n  └── 底部\"相关页面\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 导航元素\n\n| 元素 | 位置 | 作用 |\n|------|------|------|\n| MEMORY.md | 根目录 | 全局入口 |\n| 面包屑 | 页面顶部 | 当前位置 |\n| 目录 | 页面开头 | 快速跳转 |\n| 相关页面 | 页面底部 | 关联内容 |\n| 上一页/下一页 | 页面底部 | 顺序浏览 |\n\n---\n\n## 快速导航命令\n\n```bash\n# 列出所有页面\nls *.md | head -20\n\n# 随机打开一个页面\nshuf -n 1 -e *.md | xargs open\n```\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[index-optimization]] — 索引优化\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/navigation-design.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":92022,"output":388,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92410,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775843579595,"responseId":"chatcmpl-bc2648c3-de5d-40c3-bc82-1304d42a28f4"}}
