{"type":"message","id":"0bf980f0","parentId":"7781836d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:53:12.110Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Continue with rounds 43-45:\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a2d3da0642084500b7918d6e","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Visualization\ntype: concept\nstatus: reference\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [visualization, charts, graphs]\n---\n\n# 📈 Visualization\n\n> 可视化\n\n## 可视化方式\n\n| 方式 | 工具 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Graph View | Obsidian | 页面关系图 |\n| 表格 | Markdown | 对比数据 |\n| 图表 | Mermaid/PlantUML | 流程图 |\n| 时间线 | Mermaid | 时间轴 |\n\n---\n\n## Mermaid 示例\n\n### 流程图\n\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    A[用户] --> B[Wiki]\n    B --> C{找到?}\n    C -->|是| D[返回答案]\n    C -->|否| E[告知不存在]\n```\n\n### 序列图\n\n```mermaid\nsequenceDiagram\n    User->>AI: 提问\n    AI->>Wiki: 搜索\n    Wiki-->>AI: 返回结果\n    AI-->>User: 回答\n```\n\n---\n\n## 图表工具\n\n| 工具 | 类型 | 集成 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Mermaid | 多种 | Obsidian 原生 |\n| PlantUML | 多种 | 插件 |\n| Chart.js | 统计图 | HTML 导出 |\n| Python | 任意 | Jupyter |\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[knowledge-graph]] — 知识图谱\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/visualization.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":92451,"output":373,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92824,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775843585989,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2728eb0e-8dd4-4825-977d-aadf70879d58"}}
