{"type":"message","id":"de737275","parentId":"87a6ce98","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:53:39.650Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Round 45 - Feedback mechanism:\n\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7886f177e8c7a470e1c2dbf27a2f","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Feedback Mechanism\ntype: process\nstatus: draft\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [feedback, improvement, user-input]\n---\n\n# 💬 Feedback Mechanism\n\n> 反馈机制\n\n## 反馈类型\n\n| 类型 | 来源 | 处理 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 用户纠正 | 用户说我错了 | 写入 corrections.md |\n| 用户补充 | 用户补充信息 | 更新页面 |\n| 用户建议 | 用户建议改进 | 评估后执行 |\n| 系统问题 | Lint 报错 | 立即修复 |\n\n---\n\n## 反馈流程\n\n### 用户纠正\n\n```\n用户: \"你说得不对\"\n    ↓\n我: 承认错误\n    ↓\n写入 corrections.md\n    ↓\n更新相关页面 (如需要)\n    ↓\n感谢用户\n```\n\n### 用户建议\n\n```\n用户: \"建议添加 X\"\n    ↓\n评估: X 是否有价值\n    ↓\n有价值 → 创建/更新\n    ↓\n回复用户进展\n```\n\n---\n\n## 反馈记录格式\n\n```markdown\n## [2026-04-11] 反馈\n\n### 来源\n用户\n\n### 内容\n[具体反馈]\n\n### 处理\n[已执行的操作]\n\n### 结果\n[页面已更新 / 评估后暂不采纳]\n```\n\n---\n\n## 持续改进\n\n- 每周回顾反馈\n- 识别重复问题\n- 优化流程避免同类错误\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[corrections]] — 错误记录\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/feedback-mechanism.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":6761,"output":375,"cacheRead":86400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93536,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775843597715,"responseId":"019d7886db596ecc805244e967f997c5"}}
