{"type":"message","id":"2f61dff1","parentId":"06b3335f","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:53:53.395Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Continue with rounds 47-50:\n\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_59f7df902ecd40329db5545d","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Cross-Wiki Links\ntype: concept\nstatus: draft\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [cross-wiki, linking, external]\n---\n\n# 🔗 Cross-Wiki Links\n\n> 跨 Wiki 链接\n\n## 场景\n\n| 场景 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 个人多 Wiki | 工作 Wiki ↔ 生活 Wiki |\n| 团队 Wiki | 各团队 Wiki 互链 |\n| 公开 Wiki | 链接到外部资源 |\n\n---\n\n## 链接格式\n\n### 内部 Wiki\n\n```markdown\n[[openclaw]] — 内部链接\n```\n\n### 跨 Wiki\n\n```markdown\n[工作 Wiki 主页](file:///path/to/work-wiki/index.md)\n[团队 A Wiki](file:///path/to/team-a/)\n```\n\n### 外部链接\n\n```markdown\n[Claude Code](https://claude.com)\n[OpenClaw 文档](https://docs.openclaw.ai)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 链接管理\n\n```bash\n# 检查跨 Wiki 链接有效性\ngrep -roh 'file://' *.md | sort -u\n\n# 检查外部链接\ngrep -roh 'https://' *.md | sort -u | while read url; do\n  curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code} $url\\n\" --max-time 10\ndone\n```\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[backlinks]] — 反向链接\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/cross-wiki-links.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":94160,"output":372,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94532,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775843627255,"responseId":"chatcmpl-047ab29b-135a-4b8d-a3c7-c5088e936f9b"}}
