{"type":"message","id":"30a61c1c","parentId":"6d4a4ee3","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:54:32.432Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now the final round 50 - Complete checklist:\n\n\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3e9d0b2f2cb34387bbdb8ce4","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ntitle: Complete Checklist\ntype: process\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [checklist, final, complete]\n---\n\n# ✅ Complete Checklist\n\n> 完整检查清单\n\n## 新建 Wiki 检查\n\n- [ ] 创建 `memory/` 目录\n- [ ] 创建 MEMORY.md 入口\n- [ ] 创建 `entities/` 目录\n- [ ] 添加 frontmatter 模板\n- [ ] 初始化 Git\n\n---\n\n## 内容检查\n\n- [ ] 每页有 title\n- [ ] 每页有 type\n- [ ] 每页有 status\n- [ ] 每页有 last_updated\n- [ ] 每页有相关链接\n- [ ] 无死链\n\n---\n\n## 维护检查\n\n- [ ] 每周运行 Lint\n- [ ] 每月备份\n- [ ] 每季度审核质量\n\n---\n\n## 快速命令\n\n```bash\n# 一键检查清单\necho \"=== Wiki 健康检查 ===\"\necho \"页面数: $(ls *.md | wc -l)\"\necho \"死链: $(./check-dead-links.sh | wc -l)\"\necho \"过期: $(find . -name '*.md' -mtime +30 | wc -l)\"\necho \"备份: $(ls -la ../backups/ | tail -1)\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[wiki-metrics]] — 指标\n- [[lint]] — 健康检查\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/complete-checklist.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":95550,"output":374,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95924,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775843666202,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e581d74a-437c-4978-a6b2-a85746bfa75e"}}
