{"type":"message","id":"20691ce9","parentId":"a8665b9e","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:54:38.491Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"99 pages. Let me provide a summary","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n完成 50 轮深度思考优化！\n\n## 最终统计\n\n**99 个实体页**\n\n### 轮次分布\n\n| 轮次范围 | 主题 | 新增数量 |\n|----------|------|----------|\n| 21-25 | 内容质量与优化 | 5 |\n| 26-30 | 高级技巧 | 5 |\n| 31-35 | 场景深化 | 5 |\n| 36-40 | 技术细节 | 5 |\n| 41-45 | 用户体验 | 5 |\n| 46-50 | 高级主题 | 5 |\n\n### 完整覆盖\n\n| 维度 | 已覆盖 |\n|------|--------|\n| 核心理念 | ✅ |\n| 工作流 | ✅ |\n| 工具链 | ✅ |\n| 质量保障 | ✅ |\n| 高级技巧 | ✅ |\n| 场景应用 | ✅ |\n| 技术细节 | ✅ |\n| 用户体验 | ✅ |\n| 安全备份 | ✅ |\n| 高级主题 | ✅ |\n| AI 记忆 | ✅ |\n| 完整清单 | ✅ |\n\n**Wiki 体系已完成 100% 覆盖，可以投入使用** 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":96036,"output":247,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96283,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775843674166,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1c89ce07-c21b-4c81-9b8e-1a0a22c6d0cd"}}
