{"type":"message","id":"778c8eef","parentId":"3beef36a","timestamp":"2026-04-10T17:58:01.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问我是否还记得需求和 LLM Wiki 原文。让我确认一下。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n记得。\n\n## 需求\n\n> **全面认真学习，进行思考，基于自身情况：LLM Wiki**\n\n- 全面学习 LLM Wiki 模式\n- 认真思考，不是敷衍\n- 结合自身情况落地\n\n## LLM Wiki 原文核心\n\n| 核心 | 原文关键句 |\n|------|-----------|\n| **不是 RAG** | \"Instead of just retrieving... incrementally builds and maintains a persistent wiki\" |\n| **编译 vs 重新发现** | \"knowledge is compiled once and then kept current\" |\n| **Wiki 增量** | \"one source might touch 10-15 wiki pages\" |\n| **维护归零** | \"LLMs don't get bored, don't forget...\" |\n| **人之职责** | \"curate sources, direct the analysis, ask good questions\" |\n| **双屏工作** | \"LLM on one side and Obsidian on the other\" |\n| **Memex 呼应** | \"The part he couldn't solve was who does the maintenance. The LLM handles that.\" |\n\n## 我做了什么\n\n| 原文要点 | 我做了什么 | 状态 |\n|----------|------------|------|\n| 实体页 | 99 个实体页 | ✅ |\n| Raw Sources | raw/ 目录 + raw-sources.md | ✅ |\n| Ingest 流程 | 完整定义 + 自动扩散 | ✅ |\n| Ingest 10-15 页 | 定义在 ingest.md | ✅ |\n| Query Write-back | query-workflow.md | ✅ |\n| Lint 机制 | 每周维护清单 | ✅ |\n| 矛盾管理 | contradictions.md | ✅ |\n| 输出格式 | output-formats.md | ✅ |\n| Obsidian | 配置详解 + Graph + Dataview | ✅ |\n| 人之职责 | human-role.md | ✅ |\n| 隐私/安全 | privacy-security.md + security-hardening.md | ✅ |\n| 成本/收益 | why-wiki.md + roi-analysis.md | ✅ |\n| 工具链 | qmd, Web Clipper, Git | ✅ |\n| Memex | memex.md | ✅ |\n| 双屏工作 | user-access.md | ✅ |\n| Git 版本 | git.md + version-history.md + backup-strategy-advanced.md | ✅ |\n| 搜索优化 | search.md + search-optimization.md | ✅ |\n| 知识复用 | knowledge-reuse.md | ✅ |\n| **AI 如何用** | ai-usage.md + ai-memory.md | ✅ |\n| 完整检查清单 | complete-checklist.md | ✅ |\n\n**完整闭环 ✅**\n\n要继续优化还是先试试效果？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":12877,"output":548,"cacheRead":82816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96241,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775843839412,"responseId":"019d7889f935124ded17901bd32ce047"}}
