{"type":"message","id":"bab45ca6","parentId":"59a63291","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:01:19.432Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已经把原文完整保存到 Wiki 中了，并且提取了关键要点。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n原文已完整记忆。\n\n## 保存内容\n\n- **原文位置**: `entities/llm-wiki-original.md`\n- **长度**: ~9000 字符\n- **包含**: 核心思想、应用场景、架构三层、操作流程、工具技巧、关键要点提取\n\n## 核心要点速记\n\n| 要点 | 原文 |\n|------|------|\n| 不是 RAG | 增量构建持久 wiki |\n| 一劳永逸 | 知识编译一次，持续更新 |\n| 规模效应 | 一个 source touch 10-15 页 |\n| 维护归零 | LLM 不嫌烦，成本接近零 |\n| 人 vs LLM | 人选源 + 提问，LLM 干活 |\n| 双屏工作 | LLM 一侧 + Obsidian 另一侧 |\n| 问答写回 | 好答案沉淀为新页面 |\n| Memex | LLM 解决维护问题 |\n\n**已完整记忆，需要时可查阅原文** 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":7156,"output":215,"cacheRead":96512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103883,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775844066313,"responseId":"019d788d5a282cddea2bc824940d38a7"}}
