{"type":"message","id":"bd51e84e","parentId":"47b3aa23","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:13:39.824Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"分析死链：1. `entity` - 可能是模板或示例，不是真实页面\n2. `feishu` - 需要确认大小写，应该是 `feishu.md` 存在吗？让我检查\n3. `knowledge-sources` - 可能在归档里\n4. `page-a`, `page-b` - 测试/模板残留\n5. `privacy-security` - 应该在归档里\n6. `second-brain-report` - 应该在归档里\n7. `team-wiki` - 应该在归档里\n\n根据原文：\n- \"The wiki keeps getting richer\" - 但我们有孤儿页面（dead link = orphan link）\n- \"maintains cross-references\" - 需要修复这些交叉引用\n\n解决方案：\n1. 删除或修复测试链接 (page-a, page-b, entity)\n2. 对于归档的页面，添加链接到归档目录或删除链接让我检查哪些文件存在。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 思考\n\n| 死链 | 原因分析 |\n|------|----------|\n| `entity`, `page-a`, `page-b` | 模板/测试残留，应删除 |\n| `feishu` | 大小写问题？ |\n| `knowledge-sources` | 可能在归档 |\n| `privacy-security`, `second-brain-report`, `team-wiki` | 归档后链接未更新 |\n\n根据 **LLM Wiki 原文**：\n> \"The LLM owns this layer entirely... maintains cross-references, and keeps everything consistent\"\n\n修复策略：\n1. 删除测试链接\n2. 对归档内容，移除链接或指向新位置\n3. 保持 wiki 一致性\n\n开始自动修复：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6a3494fd1f5a406cbb0f4199","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities && \\\n# 1. 删除测试链接\nsed -i 's/\\[\\[entity\\]\\]//g; s/\\[\\[page-a\\]\\]/)/g; s/\\[\\[page-b\\]\\]/)/g' *.md && \\\necho \"✅ 已删除测试链接\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":108592,"output":436,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109028,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775844812614,"responseId":"chatcmpl-0d80b7e8-0e68-4f4f-9808-673f93367bb4"}}
