{"type":"message","id":"8fbe8b43","parentId":"b73f76fb","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:14:00.738Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"feishu.md 在归档里。我需要把它恢复到核心目录，因为它是系统基础页面（飞书集成是常用功能）。\n\n根据 LLM Wiki 原文：\n> \"A single source might touch 10-15 wiki pages\"\n\n这说明 wiki 是动态的，需要维护。让我恢复 feishu.md 到核心目录。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**思考结论**：`feishu.md` 被误归档，它是系统基础页面（飞书集成常用）。\n\n根据 **LLM Wiki 原文**：\n> \"The wiki stays maintained because the cost of maintenance is near zero\"\n\n恢复关键页面：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4ad5c0c941874c4983a06b95","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 恢复 feishu 到核心目录\ncp /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/feishu.md /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/\necho \"✅ 已恢复 feishu.md\"\n\n# 再次检查死链\ncd /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities\nDEAD=0\nfor link in $(grep -roh '\\[\\[[a-z0-9-]*\\]\\]' *.md | sed 's/\\[\\[//;s/\\]\\]//g' | sort -u); do\n  if [ ! -f \"${link}.md\" ] && [ \"$link\" != \"entity\" ]; then\n    echo \"❌ [[$link]]\"\n    DEAD=$((DEAD + 1))\n  fi\ndone\necho \"\"\necho \"剩余死链: $DEAD 个\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":109463,"output":329,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109792,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775844835102,"responseId":"chatcmpl-43254cd6-c0d3-4d59-8af9-cc54baf8a77c"}}
