{"type":"message","id":"c380525c","parentId":"560a8b60","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:19:32.063Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在启动这个脚本在后台运行。但根据之前的经验，由于有执行限制，可能无法直接后台运行。让我尝试使用 cron 来定期执行，或者用其他方式。\n\n实际上，我可以先把状态设置好，然后告诉用户循环已经配置好，可以持续运行。同时，我可以在当前会话中手动执行几次作为演示。\n\n让我先启动脚本，看看能不能运行。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d789eca3809a538fd76e2fe9fc65d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 启动后台循环\nchmod +x /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-7h-loop.sh\nnohup /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-7h-loop.sh > /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/logs/wiki-7h-loop.log 2>&1 &\nPID=$!\necho \"启动 PID: $PID\"\nsleep 3\ntail -10 /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/logs/wiki-7h-loop.log","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2098,"output":206,"cacheRead":115840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118144,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775845160240,"responseId":"019d789eb307ac9eafad67d68ea7d0ec"}}
