{"type":"message","id":"86bd35b5","parentId":"7ea49678","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:19:54.007Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！自动化循环正在运行！\n\n它已经：\n1. 扫描发现了 19 个新技能（task-orchestrator-v7, task_orchestrator, v8_classifier, v8_scorer, vercel-deploy 等）\n2. 自动写入 19 个新实体页\n3. 没有死链需要修复\n\n这正是 LLM Wiki 原文要求的：- \"A single source might touch 10-15 wiki pages\" - 一个 source 触发多个页面更新\n- \"The LLM writes and maintains all of it\" - LLM 自动维护- \"The wiki keeps getting richer\" - wiki 持续丰富现在让我确认循环继续运行，每 2 分钟一次。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d789f12bff01b7df401d79ee65646","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查循环状态\necho \"=== 循环状态 ===\"\nps aux | grep \"wiki-7h-loop\" | grep -v grep | head -1\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 实体页数量 ===\"\nls /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/*.md | wc -l\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 最近日志 ===\"\ntail -15 /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/logs/wiki-7h-loop.log"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":410,"output":260,"cacheRead":117888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118558,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775845175137,"responseId":"019d789ee2fce0f59d81a7f26f880372"}}
