{"type":"message","id":"99e16488","parentId":"ea99ec34","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:21:28.419Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看到问题了！循环把 docs/ 下的 Claude Code 文档全部作为实体页写入了，这些应该只是作为原始来源 (raw sources)，不应该变成独立的实体页。\n\n这是因为代码没有正确区分：\n- skills/ 中的技能目录 → 应该创建实体页\n- docs/ 中的文档 → 应该作为 raw sources，不是实体页\n\n需要修复这个问题。让我先停止循环，然后修复代码。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n发现问题：循环错误地把 `docs/` 文档也写成了实体页，这些应该是 **Raw Sources**，不是实体页。\n\n根据 **LLM Wiki 原文**：\n> \"Raw sources — your curated collection of source documents. Articles, papers... These are immutable — the LLM reads from them but never modifies them.\"\n\n需要修复逻辑 - docs/ 是只读源，不是实体页：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d78a07ea7dddf3d17e6c60ea29b91","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 停止当前循环\nkill 64789 2>/dev/null\necho \"已停止循环\"\n\n# 重新分类：将Claude Code文档移到raw，并将错误创建的实体页移动到归档\n# docs/ 下的文档应该是 raw sources，不是 entities\n\n# 1. 将错误的 docs 实体页移到归档\ncd /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities\nfor f in claude-code-*.md; do\n  if [ -f \"$f\" ]; then\n    mv \"$f\" ../entities-archive/ 2>/dev/null\n    echo \"  📦 归档: $f\"\n  fi\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 修复后实体页数量 ===\"\nls *.md | wc -l\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 新实体页列表 ===\"\nls *.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":114552,"output":354,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116058,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775845260394,"responseId":"019d78a0338524cf42d1eddcd3fe6648"}}
