{"type":"message","id":"554fab6f","parentId":"c436f12b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:25:31.819Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求：\n1. 实体页维持在 30 个左右\n2. 每次要添加时先思考\n3. 思考如何添加\n\n这符合 LLM Wiki 原文的核心思想：\n- 不是 RAG，是增量构建\n- 但也要有质量控制\n- 维护成本接近零但不能无限制增长\n\n需要思考：\n1. 什么技能值得成为实体页？\n2. 如何筛选？\n3. 如何自动判断价值？\n\n让我先停止当前循环，然后设计一个新的框架 - 只有在经过思考判断有价值时才添加。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白，需要思考后再决定是否添加。让我先停止当前循环，设计一个**有思考的筛选机制**。\n\n根据 **LLM Wiki 原文**：\n> \"You never (or rarely) write the wiki yourself — the LLM writes and maintains all of it\"  \n> \"The human's job is to curate sources, direct the analysis, ask good questions\"\n\n设计筛选逻辑：\n\n| 条件 | 是否添加 |\n|------|----------|\n| 已有对应实体页 | ❌ 不添加 |\n| 已归档 | ❌ 不添加 |\n| 核心技能（常用） | ✅ 添加 |\n| 新技能（首次发现） | ❓ 思考后决定 |\n| 重复发现 | ❌ 不添加 |\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_06d02bb754484b02ad16bfd0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 停止当前循环\npkill -f \"wiki-7h-loop\" 2>/dev/null\necho \"已停止\"\n\n# 当前实体页数量\nCURRENT=$(ls /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"当前实体页: $CURRENT 个\"\n\n# 思考：哪些应该保留在核心30个？"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":122800,"output":368,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123168,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775845523401,"responseId":"chatcmpl-0535de7c-6321-4cd9-a4f0-2836dcb99d17"}}
