{"type":"message","id":"82124b1f","parentId":"8de52c90","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:25:41.284Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user asked me to think about how to maintain around 30 entity pages and only add new ones after consideration. Based on the LLM Wiki original text, I should have the LLM (me) think about whether to add each skill as an entity page, not just automatically add everything.\n\nThe original text says:\n- \"You never (or rarely) write the wiki yourself\" - the LLM writes it\n- \"The human's job is to curate sources\" - human directs what matters\n- \"A single source might touch 10-15 wiki pages\" - but quality matters\n\nSo I need to think: what makes a skill worth being an entity page?\n\n1. **Core vs Auxiliary**:\n   - Core: directly related to my functioning (memory, skills, model, user preferences)\n   - Auxiliary: tools I might use (coding-agent, gh-issues, etc.)\n   \n2. **Frequency of use**: skills I use frequently should be entity pages\n3. **Complexity**: complex skills that need explanation should have pages\n4. **Value**: skills that provide unique capabilities worth documenting\n\nLet me present this thinking to the user and propose a framework.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n根据 **LLM Wiki 原文** 设计筛选机制：\n\n---\n\n## 筛选思考框架\n\n### 1. 什么技能值得成为实体页？\n\n| 筛选条件 | 权重 | 说明 |\n|----------|------|------|\n| **核心功能** | 高 | 影响我运行的核心 (memory, skills, model) |\n| **常用工具** | 高 | 经常使用的技能 |\n| **复杂度** | 中 | 需要解释的复杂功能 |\n| **独特价值** | 中 | 提供独特能力的技能 |\n\n### 2. 什么不添加？\n\n| 条件 | 原因 |\n|------|------|\n| 已有实体页 | 避免重复 |\n| 已在归档 | 已有历史 |\n| 纯内部 | 不需要用户了解 |\n\n### 3. 决策流程\n\n```\n发现新技能\n    ↓\n判断：是否是核心功能？ → 是 → 添加\n    ↓ 否\n判断：是否常用？ → 是 → 添加\n    ↓ 否\n判断：是否复杂到需要解释？ → 是 → 添加\n    ↓ 否\n跳过（不需要实体页）\n```\n\n---\n\n现在让我按这个框架手动筛选，保持在 30 个左右：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_327a78a8c69b46d296cfb681","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 列出当前所有技能\necho \"=== 当前 Skills 列表 (29个) ===\"\nls /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 当前实体页 (58个) ===\"\nls /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/*.md | xargs -n1 basename"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":123192,"output":573,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123765,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775845531891,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1d54f8be-0659-487e-aa42-49d34de505cc"}}
