{"type":"message","id":"ff859c61","parentId":"9baa4adf","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:26:18.031Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to think and decide which should be in the core 30. Let me categorize:\n\n**Core (应该保留):**\n1. openclaw.md - 主项目\n2. skills.md - 技能清单入口\n3. memory.md - 记忆系统\n4. model.md - 模型\n5. user.md - 用户\n6. preferences.md - 偏好\n7. ai-usage.md - 我如何使用 wiki\n8. ai-research.md - 我的研究\n9. self-improving.md - 自我改进\n10. corrections.md - 错误记录\n11. llm-wiki.md - 模式概念\n12. llm-wiki-original.md - 原文\n13. ingest.md - 摄取流程\n14. query-workflow.md - 查询流程\n15. lint.md - 健康检查\n16. log.md - 日志\n17. raw-sources.md - 源文件\n18. search.md - 搜索\n19. obsidian.md - IDE\n20. git.md - 版本控制\n21. backup-strategy.md - 备份\n22. wiki-schema.md - 规范\n23. quick-start.md - 快速入门\n24. wiki-prompts.md - 指令\n25. system-integration.md - 系统整合\n26. contradictions.md - 矛盾\n27. auto-learning.md - 自动学习\n28. feishu.md - 飞书\n29. workflows.md - 工作流\n30. wiki-evolution.md - 演化\n\nThat's already 30 without even including individual skills.\n\nFor individual skills as entity pages - maybe only keep:\n- proactivity (主动性)\n- superpowers (开发流程)\n- skill-vetter (安全审查)\n\nOthers like automation-workflows, multi-search-engine, etc. can be mentioned in skills.md but don't need their own pages.\n\nLet me create a refined list of 30 that makes sense.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d78a4313ccd1d8ec3581b2c6535c3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 思考后筛选核心30个\n# 根据 LLM Wiki 原文：质量 > 数量\n\n# 保留的核心页面分类\nCORE_PAGES=\"openclaw.md\nskills.md\nmemory.md\nmodel.md\nuser.md\npreferences.md\nai-usage.md\nai-research.md\nself-improving.md\ncorrections.md\nllm-wiki.md\nllm-wiki-original.md\ningest.md\nquery-workflow.md\nlint.md\nlog.md\nraw-sources.md\nsearch.md\nobsidian.md\ngit.md\nbackup-strategy.md\nwiki-schema.md\nquick-start.md\nwiki-prompts.md\nsystem-integration.md\ncontradictions.md\nauto-learning.md\nfeishu.md\nworkflows.md\nwiki-evolution.md\"\n\necho \"=== 核心 30 页面 ===\"\necho \"$CORE_PAGES\" | wc -l\n\n# 移动非核心到归档\ncd /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities\nfor f in *.md; do\n  if ! echo \"$CORE_PAGES\" | grep -q \"^$f$\"; then\n    mv \"$f\" ../entities-archive/ 2>/dev/null\n    echo \"📦 归档: $f\"\n  fi\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 核心页面数量 ===\"\nls *.md | wc -l\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 核心页面列表 ===\"\nls *.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":12348,"output":708,"cacheRead":111744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124800,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775845541417,"responseId":"019d78a3dc94626bdcc812ce35dc4ab0"}}
