{"type":"message","id":"7dd7089d","parentId":"1a799905","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:26:50.090Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now I have core 30 pages. The key principle is:\n- Only add when thinking decides it's necessary\n- Keep it at 30\n- Quality over quantity\n\nNow let me create a new loop that only adds after careful consideration.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n完成筛选，保持 **30 个核心页面**。\n\n## 筛选原则\n\n| 保留 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 系统基础 | openclaw, skills, memory, model, user, preferences |\n| 工作流核心 | ingest, query-workflow, lint, raw-sources, log |\n| 工具 | search, obsidian, git, backup-strategy |\n| 规范 | wiki-schema, wiki-prompts, quick-start |\n| 自我改进 | ai-usage, ai-research, self-improving, corrections |\n| 进阶 | llm-wiki, workflow, contradictions |\n\n| 归档 | 原因 |\n|------|------|\n| 具体技能页 (29个) | 太细，可在 skills.md 中列出 |\n\n---\n\n现在创建**有思考的添加机制**：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d78a54a46ac740be8cbd79a2ee6c3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 更新 skills.md 反映变更\ncat > /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/skills.md << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Skills\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [skills, capabilities]\n---\n\n# 🛠️ Skills\n\n> 29 个已安装技能（详细页在 entities-archive/）\n\n## 核心技能（无独立实体页）\n\n所有 29 个技能记录在 `skills/` 目录，如需详细页面可从归档恢复。\n\n## 技能清单\n\n| 技能 | 说明 | 实体页 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| feishu-doc/drive/wiki/perm | 飞书 | ✅ feishu.md |\n| coding-agent | AI 编程 | 归档 |\n| superpowers | TDD开发 | 归档 |\n| skill-creator | 技能创建 | - |\n| multi-search-engine | 多引擎搜索 | 归档 |\n| gh-issues | GitHub | 归档 |\n| healthcheck | 安全检查 | 归档 |\n| proactivity | 主动性 | 归档 |\n| task_orchestrator | 任务编排 | 归档 |\n| ontology | 知识图谱 | 归档 |\n| 其他20+ | 各类工具 | 归档 |\n\n## 添加规则\n\n根据 **LLM Wiki 原文**：  \n只有核心功能、常用工具、复杂功能才创建独立实体页。  \n当前保持 **30 个核心页面**，新增需思考后决定。\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[openclaw]] — 主项目\n- [[ai-usage]] — AI 如何使用\n- [[wiki-schema]] — 规范\n\nEOF\necho \"✅ skills.md 已更新\