{"type":"message","id":"a5711ff3","parentId":"cf0a16e7","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:27:02.596Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now the core is 30. Let me summarize the current state for the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 当前状态\n\n| 指标 | 数量 |\n|------|------|\n| **核心实体页** | 30 个 ✅ |\n| 归档页面 | 27 个 |\n| Skills 总数 | 29 个 |\n\n---\n\n## 添加新实体页的思考流程\n\n```\n发现新技能\n    ↓\n思考：是否为核心功能？→ 是 → 添加\n    ↓ 否\n思考：是否常用？→ 是 → 添加\n    ↓ 否\n思考：是否复杂需解释？→ 是 → 添加\n    ↓ 否\n→ 不添加，仅记录在 skills.md\n```\n\n---\n\n**现在保持 30 个核心页面，要继续自动化循环吗？** 循环会遵循这个筛选机制，只添加经过思考判断有价值的技能。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":14133,"output":170,"cacheRead":111744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126047,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775845610206,"responseId":"019d78a4e978d52ac5bce33f6f1f20c2"}}
