{"type":"message","id":"9ca4dbc9","parentId":"a0c4701b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:29:45.917Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户的要求是更严格的筛选机制：1. 达到 30 个左右后2. 新增时先思考3. 是否可以融合/精简 合并到现有页面4. 如果可以融合，就合并，不创建新页面\n5. 如果不能融合，也不添加，也不记录这个更符合 LLM Wiki 原文的精神：- \"You never (or rarely) write the wiki yourself\" - 不要过度创建- 质量 > 数量- 一个好的 wiki 是长期维护的，不是堆积的\n\n让我设计这个机制并更新循环脚本。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白，更严格的机制：**融合优先，不创建、不记录**。\n\n根据 **LLM Wiki 原文**：\n> \"You never (or rarely) write the wiki yourself\"  \n> \"The tedious part is bookkeeping... LLMs don't get bored\"\n\n设计融合机制：\n\n| 情况 | 处理 |\n|------|------|\n| 新技能可融合到现有页 | 合并到现有页面 |\n| 新技能可升级现有页 | 更新替代 |\n| 无法融合 | 不添加、不记录 |\n\n例如：新技能 `v8_scorer` → 融合到 `task-orchestrator.md` 作为一个章节\n\n让我先手动测试融合：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7e5977317f184afdb1f95a01","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 测试：哪些技能可以融合？\n\necho \"=== 思考：融合方案 ===\"\n\n# v8_classifier, v8_scorer → task-orchestrator\necho \"1. v8_classifier + v8_scorer → task-orchestrator.md\"\necho \"   原因：都是任务编排组件\"\n\n# scrapling → multi-search-engine 或新增\necho \"2. scrapling (网页抓取) → 可考虑融合到 search.md\"\n\n# intent-enhancer → 已有类似功能\necho \"3. intent-enhancer → 融合到 ai-usage.md\"\n\n# 其他内部技能\necho \"4. classifier-health → 融合到 system-integration.md\"\necho \"5. memory-keeper → 融合到 memory.md\"\n\n# 查看现有页面内容，看如何融合\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 现有 task-orchestrator 内容 ===\"\nhead -30 /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/task-orchestrator.md 2>/dev/null || echo \"不存在，需要恢复\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":125439,"output":477,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125916,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775845776954,"responseId":"chatcmpl-57b20c44-508d-4f75-b13f-4f5779509542"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7cb057ae","parentId":"9ca4dbc9","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:29:45.998Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7e5977317f184afdb1f95a01","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 思考：融合方案 ===\n1. v8_classifier + v8_scorer → task-orchestrator.md\n   原因：都是任务编排组件\n2. scrapling (网页抓取) → 可考虑融合到 search.md\n3. intent-enhancer → 融合到 ai-usage.md\n4. classifier-health → 融合到 system-integration.md\n5. memory-keeper → 融合到 memory.md\n\n=== 现有 task-orchestrator 内容 ===\n不存在，需要恢复"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":40,"aggregated":"=== 思考：融合方案 ===\n1. v8_classifier + v8_scorer → task-orchestrator.md\n   原因：都是任务编排组件\n2. scrapling (网页抓取) → 可考虑融合到 search.md\n3. intent-enhancer → 融合到 ai-usage.md\n4. classifier-health → 融合到 system-integration.md\n5. memory-keeper → 融合到 memory.md\n\n=== 现有 task-orchestrator 内容 ===\n不存在，需要恢复","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775845785987}}
{"type":"message","id":"19ae1371","parentId":"7cb057ae","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:30:22.504Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"需要从归档恢复 task-orchestrator，然后进行融合。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d78a843f5bdd9d795f026eab366a9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 从归档恢复需要融合的页面\nARCHIVE=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive\"\nENTITIES=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities\"\n\n# 恢复 task-orchestrator-v7 和 task_orchestrator\ncp $ARCHIVE/task-orchestrator-v7.md $ENTITIES/ 2>/dev/null && echo \"✅ 恢复 task-orchestrator-v7\"\ncp $ARCHIVE/task_orchestrator.md $ENTITIES/ 2>/dev/null && echo \"✅ 恢复 task_orchestrator\"\n\n# 合并成一个 task-orchestrator.md\ncat > $ENTITIES/task-orchestrator.md << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Task Orchestrator\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [orchestrator, task, scoring]\n---\n\n# ⚙️ Task Orchestrator\n\n> 任务编排与评分系统\n\n## 概述\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| **版本** | v8.0 |\n| **路由端口** | localhost:3102 |\n| **分类端口** | localhost:3104 |\n\n## 核心组件\n\n### 1. 评分 (v8_scorer)\n\n评分服务：`http://localhost:3103/api/score`\n\n6 因子评分：logic, risk, duration, resource, uncertainty, dependency\n\n### 2. 分类 (v8_classifier)\n\n分类服务：`http://localhost:3104/classify`\n\n场景标签：task_multi_step, fault_recovery, chitchat, vague_request...\n\n### 3. 路由策略\n\n| 分数 | 策略 | 超时 | 内存 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| ≤20 | DIRECT | 30s | - |\n| 21-40 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s | 1024MB |\n| 41-60 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 60-180s | 2048MB |\n| 61-80 | PARALLEL_SHARDS | 120-160s | 2048MB |\n| >80 | MEGA_TASK | 7200s | 8192MB |\n\n## 文件位置\n\n- `task_orchestrator/` - v8 完整实现\n- `task-orchestrator-v7/` - v7 版本\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[llm-wiki]] — LLM Wiki 模式\n- [[ai-usage]] — AI 如何使用\n\nEOF\necho \"✅ 合并为 task-orchestrator.md\"\n\n# 删除单独的恢复文件\nrm -f $ENTITIES/task-orchestrator-v7.md $ENTITIES/task_orchestrator.md 2>/dev/null\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 当前实体页数量 ===\"\nls $ENTITIES/*.md | wc -l"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3281,"output":622,"cacheRead":122624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126527,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775845786001,"responseId":"019d78a8356642834ae4954d16ff9791"}}
