{"type":"message","id":"58d49cc4","parentId":"8d330008","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:30:50.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完成了融合优先的机制设计。现在总结一下状态。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 完成融合优先机制\n\n### 最终状态\n\n| 指标 | 数量 |\n|------|------|\n| **核心实体页** | 31 个 ✅ |\n| 融合操作 | 已执行 |\n\n### 融合方案\n\n| 新技能 | 处理方式 |\n|--------|----------|\n| v8_classifier + v8_scorer | 合并 → task-orchestrator.md |\n| memory-keeper | 合并 → memory.md |\n| intent-enhancer | 合并 → ai-usage.md |\n| classifier-health | 合并 → system-integration.md |\n| scrapling | 合并 → search.md |\n| elite-longterm-memory | 合并 → memory.md |\n\n### 核心页面 (31)\n\n```\nai-research, ai-usage, auto-learning, backup-strategy\ncontradictions, corrections, feishu, git, ingest, lint\nllm-wiki-original, llm-wiki, log, memory, model, obsidian\nopenclaw, preferences, query-workflow, quick-start\nraw-sources, search, self-improving, skills\nsystem-integration, task-orchestrator, user\nwiki-evolution, wiki-prompts, wiki-schema, workflow\n```\n\n---\n\n**机制总结：**\n- 达到 30 个左右后\n- 新增时先思考是否可以融合\n- 可以融合 → 合并到现有页面\n- 不可以融合 → 不添加、不记录\n- 保持核心 30 个高质量页面\n\n要启动新的自动化循环吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":4717,"output":318,"cacheRead":122624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127659,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775845832570,"responseId":"019d78a82fdaa11f07057397d211525c"}}
