{"type":"message","id":"df7e6305","parentId":"5ab30ece","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:45:11.373Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"对原文不是原文核心\"，意思是需要对照原文详细内容进行学习，不是只对照核心要点。需要更详细地阅读和学习LLM Wiki原文，然后把每次学习的思考记录下来。\n\n让我停止当前循环，重新设计一个更详细的记录机制，每次对照原文的具体内容进行学习。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白，需要对照**原文详细内容**，不是核心要点。让我重新设计：\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cbd65bfe9c6a484c9c64c5ed","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 停止当前循环\npkill -f \"deep-cycle\" 2>/dev/null\npkill -f \"for i in\" 2>/dev/null\n\n# 读取原文详细内容\necho \"=== LLM Wiki 原文详细内容 ===\"\nhead -100 /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/llm-wiki-original.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":141912,"output":174,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":142086,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775846707063,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7b9edbdc-f1ba-4479-89b6-be67b1863bc6"}}
