{"type":"message","id":"a4a24746","parentId":"9c8b06f1","timestamp":"2026-04-11T01:44:50.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在发现了真正的问题：\n1. 矛盾: 2个页面同时说\"是RAG\"和\"不是RAG\"\n2. 数据缺口: 缺少 query, schema, index 页面\n3. 跨引用不足: openclaw.md 没有链接\n\n根据 LLM Wiki 原文，我需要：1. 解决矛盾\n2. 补充缺失页面\n3. 增加跨引用让我开始真正修复这些问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7a352b7f46b7aa5a176ab9c391e2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 第二步：真正修复问题\nENTITIES=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities\"\n\necho \"=== 修复 1: 解决矛盾 ===\"\n# 修改描述，避免矛盾\nfor f in \"$ENTITIES/llm-wiki.md\" \"$ENTITIES/7h-analysis-report.md\"; do\n    [ -f \"$f\" ] || continue\n    # 统一为\"不是传统RAG模式\"\n    sed -i 's/不是 RAG/不是传统 RAG 模式/g' \"$f\"\n    sed -i 's/是 RAG/可以类比 RAG/g' \"$f\"\n    echo \"✅ 修复: $(basename $f)\"\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 修复 2: 补充缺失页面 (原文: 缺少页面) ===\"\n\n# schema - 架构说明\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/schema.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Schema\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [schema, config]\n---\n\n# Schema\n\n> LLM Wiki 的配置文件，告诉 LLM 如何维护 wiki\n\n## 定义\n\n根据 LLM Wiki 原文：\n> \"Schema — a document that tells the LLM how the wiki is structured\"\n\n## 当前实现\n\n| Schema 文件 | 说明 |\n|-------------|------|\n| SOUL.md | AI 行为约束 |\n| AGENTS.md | Agent 配置 |\n| USER.md | 用户偏好 |\n| MEMORY.md | 入口索引 |\n\n## 对应关系\n\n| 层级 | 原文 | 现状 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Raw Sources | 不可变文档 | docs/ |\n| Wiki | LLM 维护 | entities/ |\n| Schema | 配置说明 | SOUL.md, AGENTS.md |\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[llm-wiki]] — LLM Wiki 核心\n- [[ingest]] — 获取知识\n- [[memory]]\n\nEOF\necho \"✅ 创建: schema.md\"\n\n# query - 查询工作流\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/query.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Query\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [query, workflow]\n---\n\n# Query\n\n> 问答工作流，根据 LLM Wiki 原文实现\n\n## 原文定义\n\n> \"You ask questions against the wiki. The LLM searches for relevant pages, reads them, and synthesizes an answer with citations.\"\n\n## Query 流程\n\n1. **搜索** - 查找相关页面\n2. **阅读** - 读取内容\n3. **合成** - 生成答案\n4. **写回** - (可选) 将好答案沉淀到 wiki\n\n## 写回机制\n\n原文强调：\n> \"good answers can be filed back into the wiki as new pages\"\n\n好答案应写回 wiki，形成知识积累。\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[query-workflow]] — 具体工作流\n- [[lint]] — 定期检查\n- [[llm-wiki]]\n\nEOF\necho \"✅ 创建: query.md\"\n\n# index - 使用 memory.md 作为入口\necho \"✅ index: 使用 memory.md (已存在)\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 修复 3: 增加跨引用 ===\"\n\n# 为 openclaw.md 添加链接\nif ! grep -q '\\[\\[' \"$ENTITIES/openclaw.md\"; then\n    echo -e \"\\n## 相关页面\\n\\n- [[memory]]\\n- [[llm-wiki]]\\n- [[ingest]]\\n- [[query]]\\n- [[lint]]\" >> \"$ENTITIES/openclaw.md\"\n    echo \"✅ 添加链接: openclaw.md\"\nfi\n\n# 为 llm-wiki.md 增加链接\nif ! grep -q \"相关页面\" \"$ENTITIES/llm-wiki.md\"; then\n    echo -e \"\\n---\\n\\n## 相关页面\\n\\n- [[openclaw]]\\n- [[memory]]\\n- [[ingest]]\\n- [[query]]\\n- [[lint]]\\n- [[schema]]\" >> \"$ENTITIES/llm-wiki.md\"\n    echo \"✅ 添加链接: llm-wiki.md\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 修复后统计 ===\"\necho \"实体页: $(ls $ENTITIES/*.md | wc -l)\"\necho \"孤儿: $(for f in $ENTITIES/*.md; do fname=$(basename \"$f\" .md); grep -rq \"\\[\\[$fname\\]\\]\" $ENTITIES/*.md || echo \"$fname\"; done | wc -l)\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":59434,"output":1046,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61632,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775871825226,"responseId":"019d7a34ff91f49bf4775ff6d730f4a2"}}
