{"type":"message","id":"5f92cef7","parentId":"0808fa27","timestamp":"2026-04-11T02:23:44.341Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There are still 2 orphan pages. Let me fix them and continue.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_faf85333c8694989bacd39b9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 修复孤儿\nENTITIES=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities\"\n\n# 找出孤儿\nORPHANS=$(for f in $ENTITIES/*.md; do fname=$(basename \"$f\" .md); [ $(grep -r \"\\[\\[$fname\\]\\]\" $ENTITIES/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l) -eq 0 ] && echo \"$fname\"; done)\necho \"孤儿: $ORPHANS\"\n\n# 修复\nfor o in $ORPHANS; do\n    for ref in memory llm-wiki openclaw framework; do\n        [ -f \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\" ] && grep -q \"\\[\\[$o\\]\\]\" \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\" || echo \"- [[$o]]\" >> \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\"\n    done\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 继续扩展: 错误处理和恢复 ===\"\n\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/error-handling.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Error Handling\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [error, recovery]\n---\n\n# Error Handling\n\n> 错误处理和恢复机制\n\n## 常见错误\n\n| 错误 | 原因 | 解决方案 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 死链 | 链接页面不存在 | 修复或删除链接 |\n| 孤儿 | 页面无入链 | 添加到索引 |\n| 矛盾 | 逻辑冲突 | 澄清描述 |\n| 循环引用 | A→B→A | 检查链接 |\n\n## 自动恢复\n\n运行 `auto-lint.sh` 自动修复常见问题。\n\n## 手动恢复\n\n```bash\n# 查看错误\nscripts/auto-lint.sh\n\n# 手动修复\n# 编辑对应的 .md 文件\n```\n\n## 备份恢复\n\n参见 [[backup-strategy]]\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[performance]]\n- [[backup-strategy]]\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ 添加: error-handling.md\"\n\n# 继续添加更多实践\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 创建更多实践案例 ===\"\n\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/examples.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Examples\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [example, demo]\n---\n\n# Examples\n\n> 完整使用示例\n\n## 示例 1: 添加新知识\n\n### 场景\n用户想让 AI 学习 Claude Code 的架构。\n\n### 步骤\n\n1. **添加 Source**\n   ```bash\n   cp claude-code-architecture.md docs/\n   ```\n\n2. **Ingest**\n   AI 读取并提取关键信息\n\n3. **更新 Wiki**\n   - 创建/更新 claude-code-architecture.md\n   - 更新 skills.md\n   - 更新 system-integration.md\n\n4. **记录**\n   追加到 log.md\n\n### 结果\n一个 source 触发多个页面更新。\n\n## 示例 2: 问答并写回\n\n### 场景\n用户问：\"如何配置 OpenClaw？\"\n\n### 步骤\n\n1. **Query**\n   AI 搜索相关页面\n\n2. **Answer**\n   生成答案\n\n3. **评估**\n   判断是否写回\n\n4. **写回**\n   创建配置指南页面\n\n### 结果\n好答案永久沉淀。\n\n## 示例 3: 定期维护\n\n### 场景\n每周检查 wiki 健康度。\n\n### 步骤\n\n1. 运行 `auto-lint.sh`\n2. 检查报告\n3. 修复问题\n\n### 结果\n0 错误状态。\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[ingest]]\n- [[query]]\n- [[lint]]\n- [[case-study]]\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ 添加: examples.md\"\n\n# 修复孤儿\nfor p in error-handling examples; do\n    for ref in memory llm-wiki openclaw framework; do\n        [ -f \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\" ] && grep -q \"\\[\\[$p\\]\\]\" \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\" || echo \"- [[$p]]\" >> \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\"\n    done\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 最终检查 ===\"\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/auto-lint.sh\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 脚本清单 ===\"\nls -la /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/*.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":75129,"output":923,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76052,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775874209851,"responseId":"chatcmpl-70ee3007-bc03-4b44-8d86-c1490f8b2532"}}
