{"type":"message","id":"3f9e2f63","parentId":"183f4137","timestamp":"2026-04-11T02:30:07.947Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求继续。我应该继续深入优化，看看还有什么可以做的。\n\n让我思考：\n1. 原文还有什么没实现的？\n2. 框架还有什么可以优化的？\n3. 质量还能怎么提升？\n\n继续深入...\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4b7f2f99173a49c0aabfb918","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 继续深度优化\nENTITIES=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities\"\n\necho \"=== 1. 创建完整配置系统 ===\"\n\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/config.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Config\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [config, settings]\n---\n\n# Config\n\n> Wiki 配置文件\n\n## 核心配置\n\n| 配置 | 文件 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| AI 行为 | SOUL.md | 约束规则 |\n| Agent | AGENTS.md | 代理配置 |\n| 用户 | USER.md | 偏好设置 |\n| 索引 | MEMORY.md | 入口配置 |\n\n## Wiki 配置\n\n```yaml\nwiki:\n  max_pages: 50\n  max_orphans: 3\n  max_dead_links: 0\n  auto_lint: true\n  lint_interval: 3600\n```\n\n## 触发配置\n\n- 孤儿 > 3 → 触发 Lint\n- 死链 > 0 → 触发 Lint\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[schema]]\n- [[framework]]\n- [[error-handling]]\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ 添加: config.md\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 2. 创建测试框架 ===\"\n\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/testing.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Testing\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [testing, quality]\n---\n\n# Testing\n\n> Wiki 质量测试框架\n\n## 测试类型\n\n### 1. 单元测试\n测试单个脚本功能。\n\n### 2. 集成测试\n测试整体流程 (Ingest→Query→Lint)。\n\n### 3. 回归测试\n确保修改不破坏现有功能。\n\n## 测试脚本\n\n```bash\n# 运行所有测试\n./scripts/test.sh\n\n# 运行 Lint 测试\n./scripts/auto-lint.sh\n```\n\n## 质量门禁\n\n| 指标 | 阈值 |\n|------|------|\n| 死链 | 0 |\n| 孤儿 | < 3 |\n| 矛盾 | 0 |\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[performance]]\n- [[error-handling]]\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ 添加: testing.md\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 3. 创建安全机制 ===\"\n\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/security.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Security\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [security, safety]\n---\n\n# Security\n\n> Wiki 安全机制\n\n## 安全原则\n\n1. **备份** - 定期备份\n2. **验证** - 修改前验证\n3. **回滚** - 保留历史版本\n4. **隔离** - 测试/生产分离\n\n## 备份策略\n\n见 [[backup-strategy]]\n\n## 权限控制\n\n- 读取: 开放\n- 写入: 仅 AI/自动化脚本\n- 删除: 仅手动确认\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[backup-strategy]]\n- [[version-control]]\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ 添加: security.md\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 4. 创建部署流程 ===\"\n\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/deployment.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Deployment\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [deploy, release]\n---\n\n# Deployment\n\n> Wiki 部署和发布\n\n## 部署方式\n\n### 1. 本地部署\n直接使用本地文件系统。\n\n### 2. 云端部署\n同步到云存储 (Feishu Drive)。\n\n### 3. 分布式部署\n多实例共享。\n\n## 发布流程\n\n```\n开发 → 测试 → 预发布 → 生产\n```\n\n## 回滚\n\n```bash\n# 从 Git 回滚\ngit revert HEAD\n```\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[version-control]]\n- [[backup-strategy]]\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ 添加: deployment.md\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 5. 创建数据迁移 ===\"\n\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/migration.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Migration\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [migration, data]\n---\n\n# Migration\n\n> Wiki 数据迁移\n\n## 迁移场景\n\n- 旧 wiki 迁移\n- 格式转换\n- 结构重组\n\n## 迁移步骤\n\n1. **导出** - 导出旧数据\n2. **转换** - 转换格式\n3. **导入** - 导入新系统\n4. **验证** - 验证完整性\n\n## 工具\n\n- scripts/auto-lint.sh - 验证\n- scripts/memory_keeper.sh - 迁移\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[backup-strategy]]\n- [[deployment]]\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ 添加: migration.md\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 6. 创建扩展机制 ===\"\n\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/extensibility.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Extensibility\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [extension, plugin]\n---\n\n# Extensibility\n\n> Wiki 扩展机制\n\n## 扩展点\n\n| 扩展点 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|\n| Ingest | 自定义获取方式 |\n| Query | 自定义搜索 |\n| Lint | 自定义检查 |\n| Output | 自定义输出格式 |\n\n## 插件示例\n\n```python\n# custom_lint.py\ndef lint_hook(wiki):\n    # 自定义检查\n    pass\n```\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[framework]]\n- [[api]]\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ 添加: extensibility.md\"\n\n# 修复孤儿\nfor p in config testing security deployment migration extensibility; do\n    for ref in memory llm-wiki openclaw framework; do\n        [ -f \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\" ] || continue\n        if ! grep -q \"\\[\\[$p\\]\\]\" \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\"; then\n            echo \"- [[$p]]\" >> \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\"\n        fi\n    done\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 运行 Lint ===\"\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/auto-lint.sh\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 创建高级集成: AI 问答助手 ===\"\n\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/ai-assistant.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: AI Assistant\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [ai, assistant]\n---\n\n# AI Assistant\n\n> 基于 LLM Wiki 的 AI 助手\n\n## 工作原理\n\n```\n用户输入 → 意图识别 → 知识检索 → 答案生成 → 写回(可选)\n```\n\n## 组件\n\n| 组件 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| Intent Classifier | 识别用户意图 |\n| Knowledge Retriever | 检索 wiki |\n| Answer Generator | 生成答案 |\n| Write-back Manager | 决定是否写回 |\n\n## 与 LLM Wiki 对应\n\n- Intent → Query 流程\n- Retrieval → 搜索\n- Generation → 合成\n- Write-back → 问答写回\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[query]]\n- [[auto-qa]]\n- [[task-orchestrator]]\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ 添加: ai-assistant.md\"\n\n# 修复最后孤儿并统计\nfor p in ai-assistant; do\n    for ref in memory llm-wiki openclaw framework; do\n        [ -f \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\" ] || continue\n        if ! grep -q \"\\[\\[$p\\]\\]\" \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\"; then\n            echo \"- [[$p]]\" >> \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\"\n        fi\n    done\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 最终状态 ===\"\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/auto-lint.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":78739,"output":1640,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80379,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775874577595,"responseId":"chatcmpl-edd0339e-fa39-488b-a800-36a93bcb7565"}}
