{"type":"message","id":"5037a2de","parentId":"d221f830","timestamp":"2026-04-11T04:38:06.032Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The status is still 73 pages with 0 dead links, 0 orphans, 0 contradictions. That's good but the user is right - I was going through motions without really \"thinking\" about what to do.\n\nLet me acknowledge the issue and do something more substantive - maybe actually create new content based on deep thinking about the LLM Wiki original.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n你说得对，我只是在走过场。让我真正思考并做实事：\n\n刚才 20 轮只是检查，没产生任何新价值。\n\n**真正应该做的：**\n- 发现当前页面的不足\n- 根据原文补充新内容\n- 实践融合机制\n\n现在做真正有用的：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c1beebf62c35477ca7f8b177","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 真正思考：对照原文，补充缺失\nENTITIES=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities\"\n\necho \"=== 真正思考：原文还缺什么？===\"\n\n# 检查原文提到的每个工具是否有完整实现\necho \"\"\necho \"1. 检查 Marp (幻灯片输出) - 原文提到但没完整实现\"\nif ! grep -q \"marp\" $ENTITIES/*.md; then\n    echo \"   ⚠️ 缺少: 创建 marp.md\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"2. 检查 Dataview (查询) - 原文提到\"\nif ! grep -q \"dataview\" $ENTITIES/*.md; then\n    echo \"   ⚠️ 缺少: 创建 dataview.md\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"3. 检查具体 Personal 场景实现\"\nif ! grep -q \"health\" $ENTITIES/*.md; then\n    echo \"   ⚠️ 缺少: 健康追踪\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"4. 检查具体 Book 场景实现\"  \nif ! grep -q \"book\" $ENTITIES/*.md; then\n    echo \"   ⚠️ 缺少: 读书笔记\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 补充缺失内容 ===\"\n\n# 1. Marp\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/marp.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Marp\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [marp, presentation]\n---\n\n# Marp\n\n> 原文提到: \"slide deck (Marp)\"\n\n## 什么是 Marp\n\nMarkdown 演示文稿生成工具。\n\n## 使用方式\n\n```markdown\n---\nmarp: true\ntheme: default\n---\n\n# 标题\n\n- 内容 1\n- 内容 2\n```\n\n## 安装\n\n```bash\nnpm install -g @marp-team/marp-cli\n```\n\n## 生成幻灯片\n\n```bash\nmarp presentation.md -o output.pdf\n```\n\n## 与 Wiki 集成\n\n将分析结果输出为幻灯片:\n- 对比分析\n- 趋势展示\n- 摘要报告\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[query]]\n- [[examples]]\nEOF\necho \"✅ 添加: marp.md\"\n\n# 2. Dataview\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/dataview.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Dataview\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [dataview, query]\n---\n\n# Dataview\n\n> 原文提到: \"Dataview\"\n\n## 什么是 Dataview\n\nObsidian 的数据查询插件。\n\n## 查询示例\n\n```dataview\nLIST\nFROM \"workspace\"\nWHERE tags contains \"framework\"\nSORT file.mtime DESC\n```\n\n## 查询类型\n\n| 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| LIST | 列表 |\n| TABLE | 表格 |\n| CALENDAR | 日历 |\n\n## 应用场景\n\n- 按标签查询页面\n- 按日期统计\n- 关系查询\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[search]]\n- [[advanced-search]]\nEOF\necho \"✅ 添加: dataview.md\"\n\n# 3. 健康追踪 (Personal 场景)\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/health-tracking.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Health Tracking\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [health, personal]\n---\n\n# Health Tracking\n\n> 原文: \"Personal: tracking your own goals, health, psychology\"\n\n## 追踪内容\n\n| 类别 | 项目 | 频率 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 健康 | 睡眠、运动、饮食 | 每日 |\n| 心理 | 情绪、压力、能量 | 每日 |\n| 目标 | 短期、长期 | 每周 |\n\n## 模板\n\n```markdown\n# 每日健康\n\n## 睡眠\n- 入睡时间:\n- 起床时间:\n- 睡眠质量: 1-10\n\n## 运动\n- 类型:\n- 时长:\n- 强度: 1-10\n\n## 情绪\n- 总体: 🙂 😐 😟\n- 原因:\n```\n\n## 与 Wiki 集成\n\n- 创建 daily-notes\n- 定期生成报告\n- 可视化趋势\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[scenarios]]\n- [[knowledge-graph]]\nEOF\necho \"✅ 添加: health-tracking.md\"\n\n# 4. 读书笔记 (Book 场景)\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/book-notes.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Book Notes\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [book, reading]\n---\n\n# Book Notes\n\n> 原文: \"Reading a book: filing each chapter as you go\"\n\n## 笔记结构\n\n```\nbooks/\n  {book-name}/\n    summary.md      # 书籍摘要\n    chapter-1.md    # 第一章笔记\n    chapter-2.md    # 第二章笔记\n    characters.md   # 人物\n    themes.md       # 主题\n    timeline.md     # 时间线\n    connections.md  # 与其他书的联系\n```\n\n## 模板\n\n```markdown\n# {章节名}\n\n## 关键概念\n-\n\n## 重要引用\n> \n\n## 思考\n-\n\n## 与其他章节的联系\n-\n```\n\n## 完成后\n\n- 创建书籍维基\n- 连接人物、主题\n- 与其他书籍建立关系\n\n## 案例\n\n类似 Tolkien Gateway 的个人版本。\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[scenarios]]\n- [[knowledge-graph]]\nEOF\necho \"✅ 添加: book-notes.md\"\n\n# 修复孤儿\nfor p in marp dataview health-tracking book-notes; do\n    for ref in memory llm-wiki openclaw framework scenarios; do\n        [ -f \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\" ] || continue\n        if ! grep -q \"\\[\\[$p\\]\\]\" \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\"; then\n            echo \"- [[$p]]\" >> \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\"\n        fi\n    done\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 运行 Lint ===\"\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/auto-lint.sh\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 最终: $(ls $ENTITIES/*.md | wc -l) 实体页 ===\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":93109,"output":1438,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94547,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775882264403,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9a3a3449-bdbe-48ad-bb75-626c99971d92"}}
