{"type":"message","id":"8a90c612","parentId":"403e628f","timestamp":"2026-04-11T04:47:38.369Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在需要修复这30个页面的孤儿问题，并更新memory.md索引。然后建立严格的添加机制。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3993d11e30744972958071aa","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 修复孤儿并更新索引\nENTITIES=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities\"\n\n# 修复孤儿\nfor f in $ENTITIES/*.md; do\n    fname=$(basename \"$f\" .md)\n    inbound=$(grep -r \"\\[\\[$fname\\]\\]\" $ENTITIES/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n    if [ $inbound -eq 0 ]; then\n        for ref in memory openclaw llm-wiki framework; do\n            [ -f \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\" ] || continue\n            if ! grep -q \"\\[\\[$fname\\]\\]\" \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\"; then\n                echo \"- [[$fname]]\" >> \"$ENTITIES/${ref}.md\"\n            fi\n        done\n    fi\ndone\n\n# 更新 memory.md\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/memory.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Memory\ntype: index\nstatus: active\ntags: [index]\n---\n\n# Memory Index\n\n> 30 个核心实体页\n\n## 核心 (Core)\n- [[openclaw]] - 主项目\n- [[framework]] - 完整框架\n- [[llm-wiki]] - LLM Wiki 核心\n- [[llm-wiki-original]] - 原文\n\n## 流程 (Workflows)\n- [[ingest]] - 获取知识\n- [[query]] - 问答\n- [[lint]] - 检查\n- [[practice]] - 实践\n\n## 工具 (Tools)\n- [[search]] - 搜索\n- [[obsidian]] - 双屏\n\n## 运维 (Ops)\n- [[backup-strategy]] - 备份\n- [[version-control]] - 版本\n- [[performance]] - 性能\n- [[error-handling]] - 错误处理\n- [[config]] - 配置\n\n## 记录 (Records)\n- [[log]] - 时间线\n- [[self-improving]] - 自我改进\n- [[corrections]] - 纠正\n- [[user]] - 用户\n- [[preferences]] - 偏好\n- [[ai-usage]] - AI使用\n\n## 参考 (Reference)\n- [[task-orchestrator]] - 任务编排\n- [[system-integration]] - 系统集成\n- [[skills]] - 技能\n\n## 示例 (Examples)\n- [[quick-start]] - 快速开始\n- [[examples]] - 示例\n- [[case-study]] - 案例\n\n## 演进 (Evolution)\n- [[wiki-evolution]] - Wiki 发展\n\n---\n\n共 30 个核心页面\nEOF\n\necho \"=== Lint 检查 ===\"\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/auto-lint.sh\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 建立添加机制 ===\"\ncat > \"$ENTITIES/addition-rules.md\" << 'EOF'\n---\ntitle: Addition Rules\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [rules]\n---\n\n# 添加规则\n\n> 融合优先，不超过 30 个核心页面\n\n## 核心原则\n\n1. **融合优先** - 新内容优先融合到现有页面\n2. **30 个上限** - 核心页面不超过 30 个\n3. **归档机制** - 不常用的移至归档\n\n## 添加流程\n\n```\n发现新内容\n    ↓\n判断：是否可融合到现有页面？\n    ↓ 是 → 融合，结束\n    ↓ 否\n判断：核心页面是否 < 30？\n    ↓ 是 → 添加为新页面\n    ↓ 否 → 拒绝/归档\n```\n\n## 禁止添加\n\n- 已存在的内容不添加\n- 可融合的不添加\n- 超过30个后不添加\n\n## 归档恢复\n\n需要时从 entities-archive/ 恢复。\n\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ 添加规则已建立\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 最终: $(ls $ENTITIES/*.md | wc -l) 个 ===\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":98835,"output":852,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99687,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775882845154,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1e16b7d7-1418-40a2-aab1-79c82d71aa00"}}
