{"type":"message","id":"9650075d","parentId":"01f40fc4","timestamp":"2026-04-11T04:52:18.054Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说没看懂，我需要用更简单直白的方式解释。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，用最简单的方式解释：\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7ae1425e0ad6570dad80c315b505","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 简单解释 ===\n\n## 这个 Wiki 是什么？\n\n就是一个 **AI 帮你整理的知识库**。\n\n## 两个核心问题：\n\n### 1. 知识从哪来？\n→ 放到 docs/ 文件夹，AI 会自动读取并整理\n\n### 2. 怎么用这个知识？\n→ 直接问我问题，我从这个知识库搜索答案\n\n## 一个命令：\n\n每天或需要时运行：\nbash /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/auto-lint.sh\n\n这个命令会自动：\n- 检查有没有坏链接\n- 检查有没有孤儿页面（没被链接）\n- 修复它们\n\n## 现在的状态：\n核心页面：31 个\n坏链接：0\n问题：0\n\n就这么多。\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 文件位置 ===\"\necho \"知识库: /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/\"\necho \"检查脚本: /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/auto-lint.sh\"\necho \"入口查看: memory.md\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":9394,"output":251,"cacheRead":93184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102829,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775883123247,"responseId":"019d7ae13301304f11f945aea73657ce"}}
