{"type":"message","id":"bc815a1f","parentId":"6f6b3f37","timestamp":"2026-04-11T10:02:47.832Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我详细介绍现有技能。我已经生成了报告，现在需要把它整理成更易读的格式告诉用户。\n\n让我直接读取每个技能的详细信息并整理。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7bfd8c8c7405bbd41a375bb16cdf","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 详细读取每个技能并整理\nSKILLS_DIR=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills\"\n\necho \"=== 29个技能详细展开 ===\"\necho \"\"\n\nfor skill_dir in $SKILLS_DIR/*/; do\n    name=$(basename \"$skill_dir\")\n    skill_file=\"$skill_dir/SKILL.md\"\n    \n    if [ -f \"$skill_file\" ]; then\n        # 读取第一行标题和描述\n        title=$(head -20 \"$skill_file\" | grep \"^# \" | head -1 | sed 's/^# //')\n        desc=$(head -20 \"$skill_file\" | grep -i \"description\" | head -1 | sed 's/.*description: //' | tr -d '\"')\n        \n        if [ -n \"$desc\" ]; then\n            echo \"## $name\"\n            echo \"$desc\"\n            echo \"\"\n        fi\n    fi\ndone"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":108327,"output":247,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109726,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775901746686,"responseId":"019d7bfd5d11c9b5c095c69824d47f4c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c9313855","parentId":"bc815a1f","timestamp":"2026-04-11T10:02:48.145Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d7bfd8c8c7405bbd41a375bb16cdf","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 29个技能详细展开 ===\n\n## agent-team-orchestration\nOrchestrate multi-agent teams with defined roles, task lifecycles, handoff protocols, and review workflows. Use when: (1) Setting up a team of 2+ agents with different specializations, (2) Defining task routing and lifecycle (inbox → spec → build → review → done), (3) Creating handoff protocols between agents, (4) Establishing review and quality gates, (5) Managing async communication and artifact sharing between agents.\n\n## automation-workflows\nDesign and implement automation workflows to save time and scale operations as a solopreneur. Use when identifying repetitive tasks to automate, building workflows across tools, setting up triggers and actions, or optimizing existing automations. Covers automation opportunity identification, workflow design, tool selection (Zapier, Make, n8n), testing, and maintenance. Trigger on automate, automation, workflow automation, save time, reduce manual work, automate my business, no-code automation.\n\n## classifier-health\n分类器健康检查与自动恢复机制，包含服务健康检测、自动重连、熔断降级。触发词：分类服务健康检查、熔断、自动重连。\n\n## clawdbot-filesystem\nAdvanced filesystem operations - listing, searching, batch processing, and directory analysis for Clawdbot\n\n## elite-longterm-memory\nUltimate AI agent memory system for Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT & Copilot. WAL protocol + vector search + git-notes + cloud backup. Never lose context again. Vibe-coding ready.\n\n## intent-enhancer\n增强意图检测识别隐式任务，包括故障类、问题描述类关键词和正则模式匹配。触发词：故障/卡顿/异常等问题识别。\n\n## multi-search-engine\nMulti search engine integration with 17 engines (8 CN + 9 Global). Supports advanced search operators, time filters, site search, privacy engines, and WolframAlpha knowledge queries. No API keys required.\n\n## ontology\nTyped knowledge graph for structured agent memory. Always active when user mentions: tasks, todo, pending, unresolved, problem, issue, need to do, should do, remember, recall, memory, 记得, 记住, 待办, 问题, 没解决, 有什么, 查询, 搜索 - handles entity creation, querying, linking, and cross-skill data access.\n\n## openclaw-github-assistant\nQuery and manage GitHub repositories - list repos, check CI status, create issues, search repos, and view recent activity.\n\n## proactivity\nAnticipates needs, keeps work moving, and improves through use so the agent gets more proactive over time.\n\n## productivity-automation-kit\n效率自动化工具箱 — 自动化工作流模板 + 日程管理助手 + 任务提醒工具 + 数据整理自动化。整合热门Skill功能，帮助用户识别自动化机会、设计工作流、管理日程、追踪任务、整理数据。触发词：效率自动化、工作流模板、日程管理、任务提醒、数据整理自动化、每天提醒、每周计划、自动化流程、省时工具。\n\n## self-improving\nSelf-reflection + Self-criticism + Self-learning + Self-organizing memory. Agent evaluates its own work, catches mistakes, and improves permanently. Use when (1) a command, tool, API, or operation fails; (2) the user corrects you or rejects your work; (3) you realize your knowledge is outdated or incorrect; (4) you discover a better approach; (5) the user explicitly installs or references the skill for the current task.\n\n## skill-vetter\nSecurity-first vetting protocol for AI agent skills. Never install a skill without vetting it first.\n\n## superpowers\nSpec-first, TDD, subagent-driven software development workflow.\n\n## vercel-deploy\nDeploy and manage Vercel projects. Use when deploying applications to Vercel, managing environment variables, checking deployment status, viewing logs."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":261,"aggregated":"=== 29个技能详细展开 ===\n\n## agent-team-orchestration\nOrchestrate multi-agent teams with defined roles, task lifecycles, handoff protocols, and review workflows. Use when: (1) Setting up a team of 2+ agents with different specializations, (2) Defining task routing and lifecycle (inbox → spec → build → review → done), (3) Creating handoff protocols between agents, (4) Establishing review and quality gates, (5) Managing async communication and artifact sharing between agents.\n\n## automation-workflows\nDesign and implement automation workflows to save time and scale operations as a solopreneur. Use when identifying repetitive tasks to automate, building workflows across tools, setting up triggers and actions, or optimizing existing automations. Covers automation opportunity identification, workflow design, tool selection (Zapier, Make, n8n), testing, and maintenance. Trigger on automate, automation, workflow automation, save time, reduce manual work, automate my business, no-code automation.\n\n## classifier-health\n分类器健康检查与自动恢复机制，包含服务健康检测、自动重连、熔断降级。触发词：分类服务健康检查、熔断、自动重连。\n\n## clawdbot-filesystem\nAdvanced filesystem operations - listing, searching, batch processing, and directory analysis for Clawdbot\n\n## elite-longterm-memory\nUltimate AI agent memory system for Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT & Copilot. WAL protocol + vector search + git-notes + cloud backup. Never lose context again. Vibe-coding ready.\n\n## intent-enhancer\n增强意图检测识别隐式任务，包括故障类、问题描述类关键词和正则模式匹配。触发词：故障/卡顿/异常等问题识别。\n\n## multi-search-engine\nMulti search engine integration with 17 engines (8 CN + 9 Global). Supports advanced search operators, time filters, site search, privacy engines, and WolframAlpha knowledge queries. No API keys required.\n\n## ontology\nTyped knowledge graph for structured agent memory. Always active when user mentions: tasks, todo, pending, unresolved, problem, issue, need to do, should do, remember, recall, memory, 记得, 记住, 待办, 问题, 没解决, 有什么, 查询, 搜索 - handles entity creation, querying, linking, and cross-skill data access.\n\n## openclaw-github-assistant\nQuery and manage GitHub repositories - list repos, check CI status, create issues, search repos, and view recent activity.\n\n## proactivity\nAnticipates needs, keeps work moving, and improves through use so the agent gets more proactive over time.\n\n## productivity-automation-kit\n效率自动化工具箱 — 自动化工作流模板 + 日程管理助手 + 任务提醒工具 + 数据整理自动化。整合热门Skill功能，帮助用户识别自动化机会、设计工作流、管理日程、追踪任务、整理数据。触发词：效率自动化、工作流模板、日程管理、任务提醒、数据整理自动化、每天提醒、每周计划、自动化流程、省时工具。\n\n## self-improving\nSelf-reflection + Self-criticism + Self-learning + Self-organizing memory. Agent evaluates its own work, catches mistakes, and improves permanently. Use when (1) a command, tool, API, or operation fails; (2) the user corrects you or rejects your work; (3) you realize your knowledge is outdated or incorrect; (4) you discover a better approach; (5) the user explicitly installs or references the skill for the current task.\n\n## skill-vetter\nSecurity-first vetting protocol for AI agent skills. Never install a skill without vetting it first.\n\n## superpowers\nSpec-first, TDD, subagent-driven software development workflow.\n\n## vercel-deploy\nDeploy and manage Vercel projects. Use when deploying applications to Vercel, managing environment variables, checking deployment status, viewing logs.","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775901768132}}
{"type":"message","id":"dd3c8ff8","parentId":"c9313855","timestamp":"2026-04-11T10:03:03.468Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我整理成更清晰的格式给用户。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 29个技能详细介绍\n\n| 技能 | 有什么用 | 怎么用 |\n|------|----------|--------|\n| **agent-team-orchestration** | 多Agent团队编排 | 设置2+Agent分工、任务流转(收件箱→规格→构建→审核→完成)、Agent间交接 |\n| **automation-workflows** | 自动化工作流 | 识别重复任务、跨工具构建流程、设置触发器(Zapier/Make/n8n) |\n| **classifier-health** | 分类器健康检查 | 检测服务健康、自动重连、熔断降级 |\n| **clawdbot-filesystem** | 文件系统操作 | 列出/搜索/批量处理文件和目录 |\n| **elite-longterm-memory** | 终极长期记忆 | WAL协议+向量搜索+git-notes+云备份，保持上下文 |\n| **intent-enhancer** | 隐式意图识别 | 识别故障/卡顿/异常等隐式任务关键词 |\n| **multi-search-engine** | 多引擎搜索 | 17个搜索引擎(8中文+9英文)，高级搜索符，无需API |\n| **ontology** | 知识图谱 | 结构化Agent记忆，处理任务/待办/问题/记忆等关键词 |\n| **openclaw-github-assistant** | GitHub管理 | 查仓库、CI状态、创issue、搜索、查看动态 |\n| **proactivity** | 主动性 | 预测需求、保持工作推进、自我修复 |\n| **productivity-automation-kit** | 效率自动化箱 | 自动化模板+日程+提醒+数据整理 |\n| **self-improving** | 自我改进 | 自省+自批评+自学习+自组织记忆，永久改进 |\n| **skill-vetter** | 技能安全审查 | 安全优先，安装技能前必须审查 |\n| **superpowers** | AI编码工作流 | 规格先行、TDD、Agent驱动开发 |\n| **vercel-deploy** | Vercel部署 | 部署项目、管理环境变量、查看状态和日志 |\n\n---\n\n### 无详细文档的技能 (14个)\n```\nclaude-code-architecture\nclaude-code-commands\nclaude-code-security\nclaude-code-telemetry\nclaude-code-tools\ncritical-interceptor\nmemory-keeper\nscene-classifier\nscrapling\ntask-orchestrator-v7\ntask_orchestrator\nv8_classifier\nv8_scorer\ngithub-manager\n```\n\n---\n\n### 使用方式\n直接告诉我需要什么，比如：\n- \"帮我部署到 Vercel\" → 调用 vercel-deploy\n- \"帮我搜索xxx\" → 调用 multi-search-engine\n- \"帮我管理GitHub\" → 调用 github-assistant\n\n**要我详细展开哪个？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":110552,"output":570,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111122,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775901768148,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d6abd172-c977-464d-9692-fd6025a565a6"}}
