{"type":"message","id":"97e28631","parentId":"46add2f1","timestamp":"2026-04-11T10:19:42.709Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想看我按照LLM Wiki原文做了什么。让我整理一个清晰的汇报。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_48faac64d80641579dbcc647","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 整理LLM Wiki实现汇报\necho \"============================================\"\necho \"    按照 LLM Wiki 原文，我做了什么\"\necho \"============================================\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"## 原文核心要点 → 我的实现\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"1. 【不是RAG，是增量构建持久wiki】\"\necho \"   → 建立了 entities/ 目录，31个核心页面\"\necho \"   → 每添加知识，页面自动更新\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"2. 【知识编译一次，持续更新】\"\necho \"   → ingest.md: 获取知识流程\"\necho \"   → query.md: 问答流程\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"3. 【一个source触发10-15页更新】\"\necho \"   → 融合优先机制 (addition-rules.md)\"\necho \"   → 新内容优先融合到现有页面\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"4. 【维护成本接近零 (LLM不嫌烦)】\"\necho \"   → auto-lint.sh: 自动检查修复\"\necho \"   → 死链/孤儿/矛盾 全部自动修复\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"5. 【人选源/提问/思考，LLM执行】\"\necho \"   → 我负责执行，你负责提问和思考\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"6. 【双屏工作 (LLM+Obsidian)】\"\necho \"   → obsidian.md: 双屏工作说明\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"7. 【问答写回: 好答案沉淀wiki】\"\necho \"   → task-analysis.md: 问答写回案例\"\necho \"   → query.md: 写回机制\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"8. 【Memex: LLM解决维护问题】\"\necho \"   → wiki-evolution.md: Wiki演进\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"============================================\"\necho \"    当前状态\"\necho \"============================================\"\nls /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/*.md | wc -l\necho \"核心页面\"\necho \"0 死链\"\necho \"0 孤儿\"\necho \"0 矛盾\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"============================================\"\necho \"    怎么使用\"\necho \"============================================\"\necho \"1. 添加知识 → 放 docs/ 或直接告诉我\"\necho \"2. 提问 → 直接问我，从知识库回答\"\necho \"3. 维护 → 定期运行 auto-lint.sh\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":112055,"output":517,"