{"type":"message","id":"70cdd9a1","parentId":"e436153d","timestamp":"2026-04-11T11:57:20.920Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about using MiniMax 2.5 and DeepSeek V3.2 for an automatic routing system in OpenClaw. They want to know preferences for architecture design.\n\nLet me think about what I know about these models and the routing:\n1. MiniMax 2.5 - this is likely a model from MiniMax\n2. DeepSeek V3.2 - this is DeepSeek's V3 model version\n\nThe user wants to design an automatic routing system that routes queries to different models based on some criteria.\n\nFor the routing architecture, I need to understand:\n1. What are the strengths of each model?\n2. What criteria should be used for routing?\n3. What is the user's preference for this architecture?\n\nLet me provide a clear analysis based on the LLM Wiki pattern and user's preferences.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0cf7c6f2716c4824b5b444a9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查当前配置的模型\necho \"=== 当前配置 ===\"\necho \"default_model: volcengine-plan/doubao-seed-2.0-pro\"\necho \"coding: codingplan/minimax-m2.5\"\necho \"cloud: deepseek/deepseek-chat\"\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 可用模型分析 ===\"\necho \"## MiniMax 2.5\"\necho \"优势: 代码能力强 (coding 模型)\"\necho \"用途: 编程任务、复杂逻辑\"\necho \"\"\necho \"## DeepSeek V3\"\necho \"优势: 对话能力强 (cloud 模型)\"  \necho \"用途: 日常问答、简单任务\"\necho \"\"\necho \"## 路由策略建议\"\necho \"1. 编程/代码 → MiniMax 2.5\"\necho \"2. 日常问答 → DeepSeek V3\"\necho \"3. 复杂推理 → MiniMax 2.5\"\necho \"\"\necho \"需要我设计具体架构吗？\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":114037,"output":386,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114423,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775908633811,"responseId":"chatcmpl-6031fd47-88c3-4d7e-a539-8003d62069d0"}}
