{"type":"message","id":"878d30d8","parentId":"8e35b0ce","timestamp":"2026-04-11T11:57:45.331Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Based on memory:\n- The user likes concise, direct answers\n- They prefer Python code examples\n- They want high-quality, high-performance, highly robust solutions\n- They want me to think deeply first, then solve problems fully automatically\n\nLet me provide a concise architecture design for the routing system:\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 自动路由架构设计\n\n### 路由策略\n\n| 任务类型 | 模型 | 原因 |\n|----------|------|------|\n| 编程/代码 | MiniMax 2.5 | 强代码能力 |\n| 复杂逻辑 | MiniMax 2.5 | 推理能力强 |\n| 日常问答 | DeepSeek V3 | 对话成本低 |\n| 简单查询 | DeepSeek V3 | 速度快 |\n\n### 简单架构\n\n```\n用户请求 → 分类器 → 路由\n                   ↓\n         ┌─────────┴─────────┐\n         ↓                   ↓\n    MiniMax 2.5          DeepSeek V3\n         ↓                   ↓\n         └─────────┬─────────┘\n                   ↓\n               返回结果\n```\n\n### 判断规则 (关键词)\n\n| → MiniMax | → DeepSeek |\n|-----------|------------|\n| 代码、编程 | 是什么 |\n| 写一个 | 怎么做 |\n| 分析 | 解释 |\n| 构建 | 简单问题 |\n\n**要继续细化具体实现吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":113408,"output":278,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114838,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775908641106,"responseId":"019d7c6690160ab8b090f1400d2dd10c"}}
